(8, 'Payroll Preparation  & Analysis', 2500, '2022-02-12', '2022-02-26', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 10, 'images/courses/1644268964.png', 19, 0, '2022-08-04 09:21:39', '2021-12-28 10:18:21', '<p>Employee costs from payroll and other benefits are among the largest costs in any company other than the Cost of Goods Sold (COGS), rent, and depreciation. This workshop starts with introductions about the departments of HR and \'accounting and finance\' then focuses on the payroll function.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Explain how the HR and accounting and finance functions contribute to their success</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Prepare the monthly payroll and review it for accuracy</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Calculate taxes, social insurances, employee benefits, loans vacations and End of Service Benefits (EOSB)</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Reconcile payroll with accounting and audit the supporting documents for payments</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Develop monthly and annual payroll budgets</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Design periodic payroll management reports and analysis</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 12,19 &amp; 26 February 2022</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(9, 'Excel Master Advanced Level', 1800, '2022-03-15', '2022-03-29', '22:00:00', '15:00:00', 15, 'images/courses/1640687837.jpg', 14, 0, '2022-08-04 09:22:01', '2021-12-28 10:37:18', '<div class=\"kvgmc6g5 cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql ii04i59q\">\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">Excel is an essential tool for speeding up productivity and allowing you to be more efficient when dealing with a large amount of data and calculation.&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql o9v6fnle ii04i59q\">\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">In this workshop, you will learn to save time and work more efficiently.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql o9v6fnle ii04i59q\">\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">With advanced Excel tools, you can create more complex calculations and create charts and pivot tables.</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">It will help you complete your tasks and analyze your data more quickly.</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">And it will give you the ability to translate your data into tables and graphs and organize the data in different columns, tables, and rows.</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">You will also learn how to work together on separate Excel sheets.</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\">\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', NULL, 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(10, 'The Leadership Mastery', 4500, '2022-03-16', '2022-03-18', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 10, 'images/courses/1644268366.png', 12, 0, '2022-08-04 09:22:46', '2021-12-28 10:40:13', '<p>Overview :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; The workshop addresses the perennial differences between management<br />and leadership. It aims at providing participants with an overview of how to be<br />a successful leader, You will get the opportunity to discover your hidden<br />talents and practice what you learn before going back to your workplace and<br />influence people, events and your own future as a Leader</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Distinguish between management and leadership<br />&bull; Identify their strengths and leadership styles through self-assessments<br />&bull; Apply breakthrough leadership and communication techniques to drive<br />business value and become a more powerful leader<br />&bull; Implement best practices for influencing peers, managers, subordinates,<br />customers and other stakeholders<br />&bull; Explain how to effectively handle challenges such as delivering unpopular<br />news, increasing team motivation and winning hearts and minds<br />&bull; Deliver powerful messages that lead to rapid action and that control<br />emotions when facing resistance and conflict<br />&bull; Optimize internal communication and sell their organization&rsquo;s vision,<br />mission and values to their team members</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 16,17 &amp; 18 March 2022&nbsp;</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(11, 'Self Awareness & Self Confidence', 2200, '2022-03-14', '2022-03-16', '10:00:00', '14:00:00', 10, 'images/courses/1644313088.png', 9, 0, '2022-02-08 10:11:01', '2021-12-28 11:36:05', '<p>Overview<br />Healthy self-esteem and self-confidence are essential for growth and achieving<br />success. Of all the judgments you make in life, none is as important as the one<br />you make about yourself. Without some measure of self-worth, life can be painful<br />and unrelenting. This highly interactive workshop is designed to help the learners<br />discover some techniques that can help them feel better about themselves and<br />improve their self-esteem and self-confidence.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Describe the four archetypes of Self-awareness<br />&bull; Process emotions in healthy ways &amp; develop Emotional Agility<br />&bull; Develop techniques for eliminating unhealthy thought patterns and replacing<br />them with supportive patterns<br />&bull; Act more assertively and understand why this is important to self-esteem<br />&bull; and self-confidence<br />&bull; Deal with setbacks in a way that does not damage self-esteem<br />&bull; Set goals that reflect your dreams and desires and reinforce healthy patterns</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', NULL, 'Virtual', 'eg', 0),
