(14, 'Competency based interview', 2800, '2022-01-03', '2022-01-12', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 10, 'images/courses/1644267235.png', 19, 0, '2022-02-21 04:09:04', '2022-01-03 12:30:27', '<p>&bull; As &nbsp;we &nbsp;strive &nbsp;to &nbsp;attract &nbsp;the &nbsp;right &nbsp;talents &nbsp;with &nbsp;the competencies &nbsp;and &nbsp;motivation &nbsp;it &nbsp;takes &nbsp;to &nbsp;execute &nbsp;the company&rsquo;s business strategy, your role is critical in doing &nbsp;the best practices for interviewing and selection, these &nbsp;include the question to ask and the answers to look for &nbsp;and how this candidates will perform in the long term.</p>\r\n<p>&bull; This &nbsp;workshop &nbsp;is &nbsp;designed &nbsp;to &nbsp;enhance &nbsp;your &nbsp;existing knowledge and skills in talent interviewing and selection.</p>\r\n<p>&bull; The result will be consistent selection of candidates who &nbsp;have the competencies and motivation to help make a positive impact in your company.</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Use &nbsp;proven interviewing process to help you accurately select candidates who are able and willing to perform the job.&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;<br />&bull;Prepare for and conduct an interview, gather and evaluate candidate data and make an effective hiring decision.&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;<br />&bull; Use a technique- behavioral based interviewing to gather behavioral examples of candidates past behaviors, experiences and achievements.&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;<br />&bull; Use a set of interpersonal and process skills to meet candidates personal needs, build rapport, gather complete data and keep the interview on track.&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;<br />&bull; Evaluate the behavioral data you collect to determine effectiveness and relevance to the target job&nbsp;<br />&bull; Compare the data you collect with the data collected by other interviewers to reach consensus on WKHEHVWVHOHFWLRQGHFLVLRQ<br />Design and organize a complete on-boarding program for new comers to the organization.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\