(15, 'Project Management', 5800, '2022-01-05', '2022-01-26', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 10, 'images/courses/1641213137.png', 10, 0, '2022-02-25 18:53:01', '2022-01-03 12:32:17', '<p>The overall aim of this workshop is to provide participants with the necessary skills required to plan their projects by creating &nbsp;project scope statements and project work breakdown structures. Additionally, participants will learn how to develop key performance indicators for monitoring and controlling their project schedule and budget. &nbsp;<br />The workshop also aims at assisting participants in appraising the feasibility of their projects by applying capital budgeting techniques. Finally, the workshop will cover how to effectively plan project stakeholders&rsquo; engagement and manage their expectations.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&bull; Plan projects using statement of work and Work Breakdown Structure (WBS)&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;<br />&bull; Schedule projects activities and build the project network model&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;<br />&bull; Calculate project budgets and schedule variances using Earned Value (EV) Techniques&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;<br />&bull; Select the right projects using capital budgeting techniques&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;<br />&bull; Relate to project stakeholders through better negotiation and communication skills</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', NULL, 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
