(20, 'Unlock Team Synergy', 2200, '2022-01-23', '2022-01-25', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 10, 'images/courses/1644845507.png', 9, 0, '2022-02-21 04:20:28', '2022-01-03 12:56:02', '<p>This teamwork training workshop will let you discover how teams evolve, understand colleagues better, improve communication skills, play to different strengths and improve their team&rsquo;s performance</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Know more about their colleagues.</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Be able to describe what makes a high performing team.</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Understand the importance of playing to different strengths and skills.</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Recognise the need for clear and effective communication.</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Understand the challenges of problem-solving within teams</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Have taken part in team-building activities to enhance their team&rsquo;s performance.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', NULL, 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(21, 'Principles of Successful Negotiations', 2800, '2022-01-23', '2022-01-24', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 10, 'images/courses/1644271147.png', 9, 0, '2022-02-21 04:20:28', '2022-01-03 12:57:11', '<p>Overview :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Knowing how to negotiate effectively, and with confidence, is a skill that will<br />change everything. This highly interactive workshop is designed to provide<br />participants with the essential knowledge &amp; tools they need to know about<br />negotiation, step by methodical step. They&rsquo;ll also be armed with a set of<br />practical tools that you can start using right away to get better results in their<br />work and life in general.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Define Negotiation &amp; highlight its importance<br />&bull; Identify different negotiation models &amp; styles &amp; when to use each<br />&bull; Using a set of effective skills for better negotiation outcomes<br />&bull; Discover the appropriate negotiation style for each situation<br />&bull; Identify personal negotiation style &amp; other&rsquo;s</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', NULL, 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(22, 'The Alpha Leader', 4500, '2022-01-30', '2022-02-01', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 10, 'images/courses/1642276458.jpg', 12, 0, '2022-02-25 19:01:00', '2022-01-03 12:59:03', '<p>This highly interactive workshop is designed to prepare an Alpha Leader through providing hands-on tools that ensure full understanding and comprehension of the role of a leader as a source of empowerment for the team, hence enhancing the overall team performance &amp; organizational success</p>\r\n<p><strong>Our workshop will cover the below&nbsp;</strong>:<br />&bull; Identify Personality Styles &amp; how to win with different styles</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Link Leadership Styles with Maturity Levels of employees</li>\r\n<li>Develop key management competencies required for the execution of basics tasks and activities</li>\r\n<li>Set SMART Goals and evaluate performance against them</li>\r\n<li>Use Time Management Matrix to set priorities</li>\r\n<li>Apply coaching techniques to boost productivity and optimize outcomes</li>\r\n<li>Demonstrate skills of Strategic Leaders</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', NULL, 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(23, 'Customer Service Professional', 2200, '2022-01-17', '2022-01-20', '12:00:00', '15:00:00', 10, 'images/courses/1644270650.png', 16, 0, '2022-02-21 04:20:28', '2022-01-03 13:01:19', '<p>Workshop Overview :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>In this workshop we cover all the most important elements of service any person involved in direct interactions with customers should know and apply. From the necessary behavioral and communication skills to the right attitude, and including specific methods to analyze and improve the service provided.<br />We cover it all in a straight forward and effective manner that will help participants ensure customer satisfaction and delight in the most challenging situations&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Explain the importance of customer service in a competitive environment<br />&bull; Practice the techniques of managing customer expectations and delighting customers<br />&bull; Provide better, faster service and increase customer satisfaction<br />&bull; Recognize early signals of customer irritation and respond appropriately in order to quickly find a workable solution to the problem</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 17,18,19 &amp; 20 January 2022&nbsp;</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(24, 'Public Speaking : Express to Impress ( BY SPS)', 4500, '2022-02-01', '2022-02-03', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 10, 'images/courses/1644313378.png', 9, 0, '2022-02-21 04:20:28', '2022-01-04 06:57:32', '<p>PROGRAM OVERVIEW<br />◘ As young professional seeking excellence in your professional world, public<br />speaking is a vital skill to your success and your business as well. You won&rsquo;t be<br />concerned anymore about how to overcome challenges in presenting yourself<br />and your ideas in different situations.<br />◘ Whether it&rsquo;s a meeting with your managers and co-workers or communicating<br />with other departments and customers on behalf of your entity. And because<br />Such situations require a powerful set of skills to be able to express and<br />impress!<br />◘ In our program, we will help you gaining all these required skills which will<br />positively impact all other elements of your professional development journey<br />to establish yourself as a valuable member in your organization.<br />◘ You will gain more confidence in yourself by mastering your verbal and<br />nonverbal communication aspects, asking the right questions to understand<br />and validate the received information.<br />◘ You will be able to do more with less saving the most valuable asset &ldquo;Time&rdquo;. By<br />learning effective research techniques collecting as many relevant information<br />to your topic, how to analyze and organize your ideas to structure your speech<br />effectively matching your audience.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', NULL, 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(25, 'Selling Skills', 2500, '2022-02-01', '2022-02-03', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 10, 'images/courses/1644308857.png', 16, 0, '2022-02-21 04:20:28', '2022-01-04 06:58:49', '<p>Overview<br />&bull; This Workshop provides participants with core knowledge about sales as a<br />function and as a process; this means that participants will get solid exposure<br />to sales and its contribution to company growth. In addition, participants will<br />acquire several skills related to negotiating deals, overcoming obstacles,<br />resolving customer issues and closing sales.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Identify and adopt the right professional selling behaviors and skills needed<br />to maximize sales performance<br />&bull; Develop critical self-driven practices to optimize personal and business<br />effectiveness and efficiency<br />&bull; Master and implement the sales process to successfully handle objections<br />and close more deals<br />&bull; Manage customer expectations and exceed it to gain customer loyalty and<br />generate repeat business<br />&bull; Master the art of verbal and non-verbal communication to create<br />atmosphere of respect and trust in the seller-buyer interface</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', NULL, 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(26, 'Negotiation Keys for Master Negotiator', 2600, '2022-02-04', '2022-02-18', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 10, 'images/courses/1644308358.png', 9, 0, '2022-02-21 04:20:28', '2022-01-04 07:00:31', '<p>Overview<br />&bull; Everyone has to negotiate at some point in his or her<br />life. This highly interactive workshop is designed to<br />provide experienced negotiators who aspire to become<br />master negotiators with the advanced tools needed to<br />take their negotiation skills to the next level..</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Identify different negotiation models &amp; styles &amp; when to use each<br />&bull; Assess personal points of strength &amp; weakness in negotiation as well as<br />those of the counterpart to optimize negotiation outcomes<br />&bull; Apply tactics in different negotiation scenarios<br />&bull; Using a set of effective skills for better negotiation outcomes<br />&bull; Demonstrate advanced skills in commercial &amp; Sales Negotiation<br />&bull; Modify negotiation plans as well as create plan B for deadlock negotiations</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', NULL, 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(27, 'Data Analysis & Reporting Techniques Using Excel', 2200, '2022-02-05', '2022-03-05', '10:00:00', '14:00:00', 10, 'images/courses/1644308280.png', 14, 0, '2022-02-12 19:35:12', '2022-01-04 07:02:01', '<p>Overview<br />&bull; It is no surprise for corporate staff to be staff to be overwhelmed by the<br />abundance of instructed data.</p>\r\n<p>&bull; ERPs and database have evolved to a point where they can house<br />amazingly large amounts of data the question now is, what do you do<br />with this data to add value .</p>\r\n<p>&bull; this workshop will introduce business intelligence (BI), hands on, to<br />allow you to clean, normalize, interpret, analyze and report large volumes<br />of data. you will be able to establish historical relationships, analyze the<br />current situation and predict future strategies .</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Design detailed reports from multiple sets of data through a variety of sources.<br />&bull; Manipulate the data within your reports to suit your business needs.<br />&bull; Extract data from your reports to use in different functions and formulas.<br />&bull; Create an attractive chart and diagram for your business reports to help illustrate data<br />&bull; Learn the concepts of gathering, cleaning and storage of data.<br />&bull; Come up with multiple scenarios to resolve business problems within extracted data.<br />&bull; Design a data model for your large data groups.<br />&bull; Mine and uncover hidden information with DAX.<br />&bull; Use Power Queries and practice shaping, blending and exploring files in Excel`s.<br />query editor , and create completely automated loading procedures inside of Excel.<br />&bull; Use Power Pivot and DAX to explore and analyze our Excel data model.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp