(28, 'Setting Budget & Forecasting', 2800, '2022-02-06', '2022-02-07', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 10, 'images/courses/1644308772.png', 17, 0, '2022-02-21 04:20:28', '2022-01-04 07:03:35', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', NULL, 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(29, 'Super Trainer', 7200, '2022-02-06', '2022-02-27', '18:00:00', '21:00:00', 6, 'images/courses/1644308103.png', 9, 0, '2022-02-21 04:20:28', '2022-01-04 07:05:02', '<p>Overview<br />&bull; Designed in a highly interactive style, this workshop provides the<br />trainers with the knowledge and skills they need to plan and execute<br />training sessions. The journey of a trainer on this workshop starts with<br />an understanding of how adults learn and progresses through different<br />learning styles, trainer skills, learning strategies, tasks and exercises,<br />and the debriefing process.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>List various adult learning principles and their implications on the delivery<br />of training<br />&bull; Identify and develop skills required in successful trainers<br />&bull; Examine training methods and determine the most appropriate for their<br />training workshops<br />&bull; Write specific instructional learning objectives (ILOs)<br />&bull; Apply training models in the design and delivery of training courses<br />&bull; Develop blueprints for training sessions<br />&bull; Plan and deliver a training session relevant to their areas of expertise</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', NULL, 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(30, 'Risk Management', 3300, '2022-02-06', '2022-02-17', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 10, 'images/courses/1644308180.png', 10, 0, '2022-02-21 04:20:28', '2022-01-04 07:06:45', '<p>Overview<br />workshop goes through the steps management needs to consider in order to<br />identify and assess risk and decide on proper risk responses and controls.<br />The workshop ends with how to monitor, communicate<br />and report risk. In addition how to look at risk in different<br />organizational areas such as strategy, reporting,<br />compliance, operations, financial and physical risk as well<br />as risk in different industries.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Identify internal and external changes that will create risks to the<br />organization<br />&bull; Understand the relation with the board of directors through<br />governance and improve Risk-Based Decision Making (RBDM)<br />&bull; Influence internal controls by choosing the response to the risks<br />identified<br />&bull; Classify risk categories in the organization and identify the right<br />authorities to manage them<br />&bull; Analyze, assess and improve risk management practices within<br />the organization</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', NULL, 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(31, 'Crucial Conversation', 3500, '2022-02-09', '2022-02-10', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 10, 'images/courses/1644308002.png', 9, 0, '2022-02-21 04:20:28', '2022-01-04 07:24:49', '<p>Overview<br />&bull; Many &lsquo;defining&rsquo; moments in life come from having crucial conversations,<br />which we anticipate will be difficult and which we may feel ill-equipped to<br />handle. We may also occasionally be involved in amicable conversations that<br />suddenly turn sour. Having the knowledge and confidence to deal with these<br />situations can make all the difference between a relationship fortified and a<br />relationship lost, or a sale made, and a sale lost.<br />&bull; This interactive workshop focuses on techniques on how to hold such<br />conversations in a positive space when surrounded by highly charged<br />emotions. It is designed to equip you with both the skillset and the confidence<br />you need to successfully manage crucial conversations and ensure that both<br />sides have the best chance of leaving the encounter feeling happy.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Define &amp; detect a Crucial Conversation<br /> Assess your usual approach to stress<br /> Recognize the power of Dialogue<br /> Recognize personal dialogue patterns &amp; change it into positive stories<br /> Use S.T.A.T.E &amp; AAMP techniques to tell your story &amp; learn the path of<br />others<br /> Handle disagreements effectively using the ABC Method<br /> Describe and practice methods to move from conversation to actions and<br />results</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', NULL, 'Classroom', 'eg', 0);
