(32, 'Payroll Preparation & Analysis', 2500, '2022-02-12', '2022-02-26', '10:00:00', '15:00:00', 10, 'images/courses/1644307892.png', 19, 0, '2022-02-21 04:20:28', '2022-01-04 07:26:59', '<p>Overview<br />&bull; Employee costs from payroll and other benefits are among the largest costs<br />in any company other than the Cost of Goods Sold (COGS), rent and<br />depreciation. This workshop starts with introductions about the departments<br />of HR and \'accounting and finance\' then focuses on the payroll function.<br />&bull; The workshop goes through the process of preparing and calculating payroll<br />and includes the controls needed and the pre-checks necessary to make sure<br />correct data is used.<br />&bull; The workshop explains how to conduct analysis on payroll and benefits using<br />Excel.<br />&bull; The course ends with ways to prepare budgets for the department and payroll<br />and benefit costs of the corporation.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Explain how the HR and accounting and finance functions contribute<br />to their success<br />&bull; Prepare the monthly payroll and review it for accuracy<br />&bull; Calculate taxes, social insurances, employee benefits, loans<br />vacations and End of Service Benefits (EOSB)<br />&bull; Reconcile payroll with accounting and audit the supporting<br />documents for payments<br />&bull; Develop monthly and annual payroll budgets<br />&bull; Design periodic payroll management reports and analysis</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', NULL, 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(33, 'Excel Core ( From Basic to Advanced )', 2000, '2022-02-13', '2022-02-27', '18:00:00', '21:00:00', 10, 'images/courses/1644289850.png', 14, 0, '2022-02-21 04:20:28', '2022-01-04 07:28:19', '<p>Workshop Overview :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Excel tools enable us to be more productive and efficient,By attending participants will learn to leverage the powerful features of Excel from basic to advanced covering Calculation, Formatting, Analysis and Reporting&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Reviewing the basics of Formatting and Calculation tools</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &bull; Mastering Excel most important functions&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;<br />&bull; Analyzing Data and Alternative data sets&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;<br />&bull; Apply the key Excel functions to prepare data for analysis&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;<br />&bull; Apply advanced calculations &nbsp;<br />&nbsp;<br />&bull; Create and customize pivot tables to reconcile and analyze accounts efficiently&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;<br />&bull; Utilize pivot tables functions and calculations to generate a set of management and business analysis reports&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;<br />&bull; Creating Advanced charts and graphics&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;<br />&bull; Changing workbook Appearance&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', NULL, 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(34, 'Finance for Non - Financials', 2800, '2022-02-13', '2022-02-14', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 10, 'images/courses/1644402372.png', 17, 0, '2022-02-21 04:20:28', '2022-01-04 07:29:38', '<p>Workshop Overview :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>This Workshop transforms financial and accounting concepts into decision making tools you can usesuccessfully every day. You will learn to apply thefundamentals of finance to improve budget management, increase potential profits, and assess the financial performance of business activities. You will also understand the terminology used by accounting and finance staff and will feel more confident when being involved with them or using them.</p>\r\n<p>Professionals/Managers with a financial background are considered most efficient at managing any operating scenario. Knowledge of financial aspects that help in decision making is the key to their success. It is important for a senior professional to be equipped with financial decision-making tools to be able to analyze financial statements, understand the nature &nbsp;of cost and ways to reduce cost, take pricing decisions, decide a product mix and opt for the best suited option of financing the need.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', NULL, 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(35, 'The Pro Recruiter', 3500, '2022-02-14', '2022-02-23', '18:00:00', '21:00:00', 10, 'images/courses/1643661072.jpg', 19, 0, '2022-02-21 04:20:28', '2022-01-04 07:32:16', '<p>Build your strategic aspects of this important HR function. In this workshop It will show<br />you the logical and correct steps you must take to structure and implement<br />recruitment and selection practices and how to be a professional recruiter.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Define recruitment and selection and the important role this function plays in the<br />success of an organization<br />&bull; List the main steps that should be followed to develop an effective recruitment plan<br />and select the best methods and sources for attracting qualified candidates<br />&bull; Choose the most appropriate techniques for short listing and assessing candidates<br />considering the reliability and validity of each<br />&bull; Implement the right measures and Key Performance Indicators (KPIs) to evaluate<br />the effectiveness of recruitment efforts</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif;\">T:</span></strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif;\">M:</span></strong> 01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif;\">Email :</span></strong> <a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(36, 'Business Etiquette - Doing Business with Class', 2500, '2022-02-14', '2022-02-17', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 6, 'images/courses/1643661313.png', 10, 0, '2022-02-21 04:20:28', '2022-01-04 07:33:39', '<p>Although traditional business relationships and communication strategies are evolving, etiquette and professionalism remain unchanged. This is why a knowledge of business etiquette is vital. This interactive workshop introduces participants to the principles of building and maintaining professional relationships, as well as providing practical guidance for typical workplace situations. It also provides tips on how to apply proper manners and business etiquette in many different setting&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Workshop learning outcomes :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Explain how to behave correctly in Business Situations&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;<br />&bull; Demonstrate appropriate personal and professional conduct&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;<br />&bull; Apply proper communication etiquette&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;<br />&bull; Know How to represent your Corporate Branding ?</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif;\">T:</span></strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif;\">M:</span></strong> 01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif;\">Email :</span></strong> <a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', NULL, 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(37, 'Supervisory Skills', 3500, '2022-02-20', '2022-02-22', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 5, 'images/courses/1644307685.png', 12, 0, '2022-02-25 19:03:05', '2022-01-04 07:35:35', '<p>&nbsp;The workshop is designed to provide learners with highly effective tools &amp; techniques that improve the essential supervisory skills your team needs, both managerial &amp; people&rsquo;s skills - to strengthen teamwork, team performance &amp; organizational success.</p>\r\n<p>Workshop Learning Outcomes :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;Identify the supervision functions</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Create a planning network diagram</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Describe the elements of planning</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Apply the principles &amp; approaches of organizing work</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Use IDEALS Delegation Model to empower the team</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Describe the control process, types &amp; challenges</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Apply tools to fix team performance</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Demonstrate coaching skills &amp; mentoring characteristics&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', NULL, 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(38, 'Effective Delegation', 1800, '2022-02-22', '2022-02-22', '10:00:00', '18:00:00', 8, 'images/courses/1644307441.png', 12, 0, '2022-02-21 04:20:28', '2022-01-04 07:37:39', '<p>Effective delegation is one of the most valuable skills you can master. It reduces<br />your workload and develops employee skills. Delegating prepares employees<br />who work for you to be able to handle your responsibilities and simultaneously<br />allows you to advance to other career opportunities within your organization.<br />Delegation is often one of the hardest skills for a manager to master. However,<br />the skill can be learned. This interactive one-day workshop will explore many of<br />the facets of delegation, including when to delegate and to whom to delegate.<br />We will also go through the delegation process step by step and learn about<br />techniques to overcome problems</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Identify how delegation fits into your job and how it can make you more<br />&bull; successful<br />&bull; Identify different ways of delegating tasks<br />&bull; Use an effective process for effective delegation<br />&bull; Give better instructions for better delegation results<br />&bull; Recognize common delegation pitfalls and how to avoid them<br />&bull; Monitor delegation results<br />&bull; Give effective feedback</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', NULL, 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(39, 'Analytical Thinking', 2800, '2022-02-23', '2022-02-24', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 10, 'images/courses/1644307522.png', 10, 0, '2022-02-21 04:20:28', '2022-01-04 07:38:57', '<p>Overview<br />In today&rsquo;s society, many people experience information overload. We are<br />bombarded with messages to believe various ideas, purchase things, support<br />causes, and lead our lifestyle in a particular way. How do you know what to<br />believe? How do you separate the truth from the myths?<br />The answer lies in analytical &amp; critical thinking skills. The ability to clearly reason<br />through problems and to present arguments in a logical, compelling way has<br />become a key skill for survival in today&rsquo;s world. This highly interactive workshop<br />will give you some practical tools and hands-on experience with critical thinking<br />and problem solving.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Define core concepts of analytical thinking</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Describe other thinking styles, including left/right brain thinking and whole-<br />brain thinking</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Work through the analytical thinking process to build or analyze arguments<br />&bull; Develop and evaluate explanations<br />&bull; Improve key analytical thinking skills, including active listening and<br />questioning<br />&bull; Prepare and present powerful arguments</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', NULL, 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(40, 'Your Business writing Mojo !', 2800, '2022-02-27', '2022-02-28', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 10, 'images/courses/1644392318.jpg', 13, 0, '2022-02-21 04:20:28', '2022-01-04 07:41:02', '<div class=\"kvgmc6g5 cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql ii04i59q\">\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"text-align: start;\">Overview<br />&bull; In business writing, the language is concrete, the point of view is clear,<br />and the points are well expressed.<br />&bull; This workshop is designed to provide the learners with a proven step-by-step<br />process, to write faster and more effectively.</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"text-align: start;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"text-align: start;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"text-align: start;\">Learning Objcetives :&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"text-align: start;\">&bull; Apply the basic tools of writing for effective outcome<br />&bull; Understand and master the punctuation &amp;amp; spelling techniques for<br />better Business writing<br />&bull; Develop a technical writing style<br />&bull; Identify the different types of writing<br />&bull; Avoid common mistakes in technical writing<br />&bull; Demonstrate an understanding of formal language required for business<br />communication</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"text-align: start;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"text-align: start;\">\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif;\">T:</span></strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif;\">M:</span></strong> 01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif;\">Email :</span></strong> <a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', NULL, 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(44, 'Strategic Account Management', 2800, '2022-03-30', '2022-03-31', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 11, 'images/courses/1644313297.png', 16, 0, '2022-02-21 04:20:28', '2022-01-10 12:19:26', '<p>Overview<br />&bull; This highly interactive workshop is designed to raise the participants&rsquo;<br />awareness of Key Account Management &amp; it&rsquo;s best practices. Participants will<br />acquire the knowledge &amp; tools needed to Identify accounts with the greatest<br />potential for growth, developing strategies to grow them, building essential<br />customer relationships, and bring value to customers. At the same time,<br />growing sales by selling more to existing accounts.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Identify the main functions of key accounts and how they are aligned to the<br />business organization<br />&bull; Define and prioritize key accounts to measure their profitability and strategic<br />importance to a company<br />&bull; Classify customer relations levels to improve the way Account Managers<br />deal with customers<br />&bull; Establish customer focused plans and strategies needed to develop key<br />accounts<br />&bull; Determine the functional role of key account managers in facing the<br />changing challenges in the market</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>23,23,23,23</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(45, 'HR Policies & Procedures', 2800, '2022-03-05', '2022-03-19', '10:00:00', '15:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1644307566.png', 19, 0, '2022-02-21 04:20:28', '2022-01-11 04:28:10', '<p>&nbsp;Writing human resources policies and procedures is both an art and a science. &nbsp;&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;<br />This workshop will equip you with the knowledge and skills you need to complete this challenging task inhouse. If you still decide to outsource this activity, you will benefit from this course by learning how to ensure the policies and procedures produced by the third party are written in the right manner for your organization.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objcetives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; List all human resources functions and responsibilities and identify their<br />contributions to organizational success<br />&bull; Explain the difference between policies, processes and procedures<br />&bull; Apply appropriate HR policies and procedures writing techniques<br />&bull; Describe the purpose and usefulness of human resources policies and<br />procedures<br />&bull; Develop human resources policies and procedures</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Dates : 05,12 &amp; 19 March every saturday&nbsp;</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(46, 'Deign Thinking - Unlock Innovation', 2200, '2022-03-02', '2022-03-30', '10:00:00', '14:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1646044255.png', 9, 0, '2022-02-28 10:30:56', '2022-01-11 04:30:53', '<p>Design thinking is a powerful process of problem<br />solving, a journey that begins with having an empathic<br />understanding of unmet customer needs. From that<br />insight emerges a blend of Heart, Head and Hand<br />process that is based on vision, continuing on to<br />development, applied creativity, prototyping then diving<br />into experimentation, practical creation &amp; testing. This<br />highly interactive workshop is designed to help the<br />participants learn a proven, systematic approach to new<br />product development through a process that puts<br />unmet customer needs at the center of the problem. It<br />also helps them apply design thinking approaches to<br />business, so that the success rate for innovation can<br />improve substantially.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Use Design Thinking to solve problems more creatively<br />&bull; Understand problems from the customer\'s perspective<br />&bull; Apply different brainstorming techniques to identify<br />innovative ideas<br />&bull; Use effective design research<br />&bull; Understand the value of creating prototypes to test your<br />ideas<br />&bull; Keep your design ideas moving forward</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif;\">T:</span></strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif;\">M:</span></strong> 01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif;\">Email :</span></strong> <a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>02,09,16,23 &amp; 30 March&nbsp;</p>', 'Virtual', 'eg', 0),
(47, 'Supply chain Essentials', 3500, '2022-03-04', '2022-03-18', '09:05:00', '17:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1644291065.png', 18, 0, '2022-02-21 04:20:28', '2022-01-11 04:33:40', '<p>&nbsp;Supply chain management and logistics encompasses all the activities involved ingetting products to consumers including planning, storing, moving, and accounting for inventory. Inventory availability is the most important aspect of customer service, and the cost of inventory is one of the most important entries on a company&rsquo;s balance sheet. Learn to minimize inventory through understanding your customer&rsquo;s needs.</p>\r\n<p>&bull; High quality contract development and management tools are essential activities in achieving improved levels of performance for all Procurement and Supply Management practitioners</p>\r\n<p>&bull; This workshop is designed to increase the contracting preparation and execution competencies of practitioners focusing on contractual terms, types, and structure. Learn to drive cost savings and mitigate supplier risk through contracting activities. This course is perfect for practitioners responsible for acquisition of materials, labor, equipment and/or professional services.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>● Describe the objectives of supply chain management (stock control,<br />purchasing, stores and physical distribution) and explain how they relate to<br />each other<br />● Categorize stock items based on the classification models<br />● Calculate future demand for different stock items<br />● Apply the purchasing processes<br />● Identify best practices in warehouses to maintain accurate inventory records<br />● List the various transportation functions and costs</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif;\">T:</span></strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif;\">M:</span></strong> 01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif;\">Email :</span></strong> <a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>04,11 &amp; 18 March</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
