(56, 'The Power Of Positive Attitude', 2500, '2022-03-23', '2022-03-24', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1644290026.png', 19, 0, '2022-02-21 04:20:28', '2022-01-15 20:42:44', '<p>Overview<br />Positive thinking and attitudes can increase both your personal and business results and achievements. New business requirements, increased performance demands and a changing workforce mean it is essential for professionals at all levels to understand and master the skills, techniques and methods of positive thinking and positive attitude. Recent studies in behavioral science and neuroscience reveal scientific proof and evidence of the power of a positive mental attitude. Research also tells us that high achievers have trained themselves in this vital attitude. &nbsp;This interactive and highly practical workshop gives you a step-by-step method to cultivate the power of a positive thinking and attitude. It will also provide you with many practical insights and tools to manage and develop others as well.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Examine the impact of positive attitude on personal and professional<br />environments<br />&bull; List the steps needed for improving attitude and behavior<br />&bull; Apply positive psychology techniques to improve effectiveness on the job<br />&bull; Identify preferred thinking patterns and filters<br />&bull; Use techniques to improve relationships with others</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T</strong><strong>:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M</strong><strong>:</strong> 01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong> <a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', NULL, 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(57, 'Writing Proposals & Reports', 2800, '2022-03-27', '2022-03-28', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1644291093.png', 13, 0, '2022-02-21 04:20:28', '2022-01-24 14:12:23', '<p>Overview :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>It is essential to understand how to write reports and proposals that get read. We<br />write reports in a range of formats and a variety of purposes. Whether you need<br />to report on a product analysis, inventory, feasibility studies, or something else,<br />report writing is a skill you will use again and again.<br />Having a method to prepare these documents will help you be as efficient as<br />possible with the task. This highly interactive workshop will build on a solid base<br />of writing skills to present information in formal, informal, and proposal styles.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Prepare Reports And Proposals That Inform, Persuade, and Provide<br />Information.<br />&bull; Review Your Work So That It Is Clear, Concise, Complete, and Correct.<br />&bull; Apply Business Writing Skills in Real Work Applications<br />&bull; Employ The Best Approach For Winning a Proposal<br />&bull; Describe &amp; Follow The Four Stages of Writing A Report<br />&bull; Create a Winning Design that Gets Responses</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 27 &amp; 28 March 2022&nbsp;</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(58, 'Unlock Team Synergy', 400, '2022-01-23', '2022-01-25', '11:00:00', '15:00:00', 10, 'images/courses/1644291192.png', 9, 0, '2022-02-08 03:33:13', '2022-02-08 03:33:13', '<p>Overview :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; &ldquo;No one can whistle a symphony. It takes an orchestra to play it.&rdquo;<br />Being part of a team that gets results begins with establishing a team mindset for<br />yourself as team member. For that reason, this highly interactive workshop<br />begins with a discussion of what a team is and the essential nature of the team<br />mindset.<br />&bull; From there, the workshop journey will lead you through the foundational skills<br />that make teams work, including communication &amp;amp; essential conflict<br />resolution skills to work out unique team challenges &amp;amp; resolve potential<br />conflicts among the team members..</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Describe the Characteristics of High Performing Teams<br />&bull; Understand the importance of playing to different strengths and skills<br />&bull; Recognize the need for clear and effective communication<br />&bull; Understand the challenges of conflict resolution within teams<br />&bull; Participate in enhancing team&rsquo;s collaboration</p>', NULL, 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(59, 'Data Analysis & Reporting Techniques Using Excel', 280, '2022-01-02', '2022-01-16', '11:00:00', '15:00:00', 10, 'images/courses/1644291356.png', 14, 0, '2022-02-08 03:35:57', '2022-02-08 03:35:57', '<p>Overview :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; It is no surprise for corporate staff to be staff to be overwhelmed by the<br />abundance of instructed data.</p>\r\n<p>&bull; ERPs and database have evolved to a point where they can house<br />amazingly large amounts of data the question now is, what do you do<br />with this data to add value .</p>\r\n<p>&bull; this workshop will introduce business intelligence (BI), hands on, to<br />allow you to clean, normalize, interpret, analyze and report large volumes<br />of data. you will be able to establish historical relationships, analyze the<br />current situation and predict future strategies</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Design detailed reports from multiple sets of data through a variety of sources.<br />&bull; Manipulate the data within your reports to suit your business needs.<br />&bull; Extract data from your reports to use in different functions and formulas.<br />&bull; Create an attractive chart and diagram for your business reports to help illustrate data<br />&bull; Learn the concepts of gathering, cleaning and storage of data.<br />&bull; Come up with multiple scenarios to resolve business problems within extracted data.<br />&bull; Design a data model for your large data groups.<br />&bull; Mine and uncover hidden information with DAX.<br />&bull; Use Power Queries and practice shaping, blending and exploring files in Excel`s.<br />query editor , and create completely automated loading procedures inside of Excel.<br />&bull; Use Power Pivot and DAX to explore and analyze our Excel data model.</p>', NULL, 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(60, 'Your First 90 Days as a Manager', 500, '2022-01-16', '2022-01-19', '10:00:00', '14:00:00', 10, 'images/courses/1644291545.png', 12, 0, '2022-02-08 03:39:05', '2022-02-08 03:39:05', '<p>Overview :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; As long as there have been leaders, there have been leadership transitions.<br />The changes challenges these transitions impose on the new leader are as<br />old as human society. Those challenges have not gotten any easier. On the<br />contrary, the complexity of modern organizations and the speed at which<br />business gets conducted have seemingly added to it. This highly interactive<br />workshop is your roadmap for taking charge in your first 90 days in your new<br />position as a newly promoted manager. Why do you need it? Because<br />transitions are critical times when small differences in your actions can have<br />huge impacts on results.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Describe &amp; develop new leadership competencies<br />&bull; Conduct a personal SWOT assessment to expand on the strengths &amp;<br />improve the weaknesses<br />&bull; Follow a 90-days action plan overcome the promotion challenge<br />&bull; Use the ADEPT Model to place people in the right roles &amp; provide the<br />right support<br />&bull; Define Decision-making styles &amp; employ each style according to the<br />situation</p>', NULL, 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(61, 'Customer Service Professional', 430, '2022-01-17', '2022-01-20', '13:00:00', '16:00:00', 10, 'images/courses/1644291758.png', 15, 0, '2022-02-08 03:42:38', '2022-02-08 03:42:38', '<p>Overview :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>While many organizations promise to deliver an incredible customer experience,<br />some are better at supplying this than others. This two-day interactive workshop<br />is designed around six critical elements of customer service that, when a<br />company truly embraces them, bring customers back to experience service that<br />outdoes the competition.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Define customer service and its approach<br />&bull; Understand how your own behavior affects the behavior of others<br />&bull; Demonstrate confidence and skill as a problem solver<br />&bull; Apply techniques to deal with difficult customers<br />&bull; Know how to provide excellent customer service</p>', NULL, 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(62, 'Principles of successful Negotiator', 430, '2022-01-23', '2022-01-26', '12:00:00', '15:00:00', 10, 'images/courses/1644291877.png', 9, 0, '2022-02-08 03:44:37', '2022-02-08 03:44:37', '<p>Overview :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Knowing how to negotiate effectively, and with confidence, is a skill that will<br />change everything. This highly interactive workshop is designed to provide<br />participants with the essential knowledge &amp; tools they need to know about<br />negotiation, step by methodical step. They&rsquo;ll also be armed with a set of<br />practical tools that you can start using right away to get better results in their<br />work and life in general.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Define Negotiation &amp; highlight its importance<br />&bull; Identify different negotiation models &amp; styles &amp; when to use each<br />&bull; Using a set of effective skills for better negotiation outcomes<br />&bull; Discover the appropriate negotiation style for each situation<br />&bull; Identify personal negotiation style &amp; other&rsquo;s</p>', NULL, 'Virtual', 'sa', 0);
INSERT INTO `courses` (`id`, `name`, `price`, `start_date`, `end_date`, `time_from`, `time_to`, `students_limit`, `image`, `category_id`, `disable`, `updated_at`, `created_at`, `description`, `schedule`, `type`, `lang`, `top_month`) VALUES
(63, 'The Alpha Leader', 500, '2022-01-30', '2022-02-02', '10:00:00', '14:00:00', 10, 'images/courses/1644292004.jpg', 12, 0, '2022-02-28 10:15:22', '2022-02-08 03:46:45', '<p>Overview :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>This highly interactive workshop is designed to prepare an Alpha Leader<br />through providing hands-on tools that ensure full understanding and<br />comprehension of the role of a leader as a source of empowerment for the<br />team, hence enhancing the overall team performance &amp; organizational<br />success.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Identify Personality Styles &amp; how to win with different styles<br />&bull; Link Leadership Styles with Maturity Levels of employees<br />&bull; Develop key management competencies required for the execution of<br />basics tasks and activities<br />&bull; Set SMART Goals and evaluate performance against them<br />&bull; Use Time Management Matrix to set priorities<br />&bull; Apply coaching techniques to boost productivity and optimize outcomes<br />&bull; Demonstrate skills of Strategic Leaders</p>', NULL, 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(64, 'Selling Skills', 500, '2022-02-01', '2022-02-03', '11:00:00', '15:00:00', 10, 'images/courses/1644292483.png', 16, 0, '2022-02-08 03:54:44', '2022-02-08 03:54:44', '<p>Overview :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; This Workshop provides participants with core knowledge about sales as a<br />function and as a process; this means that participants will get solid exposure<br />to sales and its contribution to company growth. In addition, participants will<br />acquire several skills related to negotiating deals, overcoming obstacles,<br />resolving customer issues and closing sales.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Identify and adopt the right professional selling behaviors and skills needed<br />to maximize sales performance<br />&bull; Develop critical self-driven practices to optimize personal and business<br />effectiveness and efficiency<br />&bull; Master and implement the sales process to successfully handle objections<br />and close more deals<br />&bull; Manage customer expectations and exceed it to gain customer loyalty and<br />generate repeat business<br />&bull; Master the art of verbal and non-verbal communication to create<br />atmosphere of respect and trust in the seller-buyer interface</p>', NULL, 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(65, 'Risk Management', 500, '2022-02-06', '2022-02-17', '11:00:00', '15:00:00', 10, 'images/courses/1644292641.png', 10, 0, '2022-02-28 09:54:13', '2022-02-08 03:57:21', '<p>Overview :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>workshop goes through the steps management needs to consider in order to<br />identify and assess risk and decide on proper risk responses and controls.<br />The workshop ends with how to monitor, communicate<br />and report risk. In addition how to look at risk in different<br />organizational areas such as strategy, reporting,<br />compliance, operations, financial and physical risk as well<br />as risk in different industries.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Identify internal and external changes that will create risks to the<br />organization<br />&bull; Understand the relation with the board of directors through<br />governance and improve Risk-Based Decision Making (RBDM)<br />&bull; Influence internal controls by choosing the response to the risks<br />identified<br />&bull; Classify risk categories in the organization and identify the right<br />authorities to manage them<br />&bull; Analyze, assess and improve risk management practices within<br />the organization</p>', NULL, 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(66, 'Excel Core ( From Basic to Advanced )', 250, '2022-02-13', '2022-03-01', '19:00:00', '22:00:00', 10, 'images/courses/1644293048.png', 14, 0, '2022-02-08 04:04:08', '2022-02-08 04:04:08', '<p>Overview :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Excel tools enable us to be more productive and<br />efficient By attending participants will learn to leverage<br />the powerful features of Excel from basic to advanced<br />covering Calculation, Formatting, Analysis and<br />Reporting&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Reviewing the basics of Formatting and Calculation tools<br />&bull; Mastering Excel most important functions<br />&bull; Analyzing Data and Alternative data sets<br />&bull; Apply the key Excel functions to prepare data for analysis<br />&bull; Apply advanced calculations<br />&bull; Create and customize pivot tables to reconcile and analyze accounts efficiently<br />&bull; Utilize pivot tables functions and calculations to generate a set of management and<br />business analysis reports<br />&bull; Creating Advanced charts and graphics<br />&bull; Changing workbook Appearance</p>', NULL, 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(67, 'Business Etiquette - Doing Business with Class', 400, '2022-02-14', '2022-02-17', '13:00:00', '16:00:00', 10, 'images/courses/1644293299.png', 9, 0, '2022-02-08 04:08:20', '2022-02-08 04:08:20', '<p>Overview :</p>\r\n<p>Have you ever had to make small talk with a Very Important Person and been<br />lost for words?<br />If the answer is yes, then you know just how agonizing some moments can be.<br />Even worse (and what can be even more damaging to your career) are the<br />social gaffes you aren&rsquo;t even aware you make.<br />This highly interactive workshop will help you handle most of those socially<br />difficult moments. You&rsquo;ll have an extra edge in areas you may not have given a<br />lot of thought to before.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Differentiate between ethics, manners and etiquette<br />&bull; Identify the significance of etiquette and manners in business<br />&bull; Develop right professional image<br />&bull; Identify how to manage the workstation<br />&bull; Describe how to behave in Open Area office set-up<br />&bull; Apply proper communication etiquette<br />&bull; Display proper techniques towards universal behavior etiquette<br />&bull; Demonstrate appropriate personal and professional conduct<br />&bull; Identify how to represent the Corporate Branding</p>', NULL, 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(68, 'Negotiation Keys for Master Negation', 2800, '2022-02-20', '2022-02-22', '10:00:00', '14:00:00', 10, 'images/courses/1644293632.png', 19, 0, '2022-02-21 04:20:28', '2022-02-08 04:13:53', '<p>Overview<br />&bull; Everyone has to negotiate at some point in his or her<br />life. This highly interactive workshop is designed to<br />provide experienced negotiators who aspire to become<br />master negotiators with the advanced tools needed to<br />take their negotiation skills to the next level..</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Identify different negotiation models &amp; styles &amp; when to use each<br />&bull; Assess personal points of strength &amp; weakness in negotiation as well as<br />those of the counterpart to optimize negotiation outcomes<br />&bull; Apply tactics in different negotiation scenarios<br />&bull; Using a set of effective skills for better negotiation outcomes<br />&bull; Demonstrate advanced skills in commercial &amp; Sales Negotiation<br />&bull; Modify negotiation plans as well as create plan B for deadlock negotiations</p>', NULL, 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(69, 'Crucial Conversation', 500, '2022-02-27', '2022-03-02', '18:00:00', '21:00:00', 10, 'images/courses/1644293774.png', 9, 0, '2022-02-08 04:16:15', '2022-02-08 04:16:15', '<p>Overview<br />&bull; Many &lsquo;defining&rsquo; moments in life come from having crucial conversations,<br />which we anticipate will be difficult and which we may feel ill-equipped to<br />handle. We may also occasionally be involved in amicable conversations that<br />suddenly turn sour. Having the knowledge and confidence to deal with these<br />situations can make all the difference between a relationship fortified and a<br />relationship lost, or a sale made, and a sale lost.<br />&bull; This interactive workshop focuses on techniques on how to hold such<br />conversations in a positive space when surrounded by highly charged<br />emotions. It is designed to equip you with both the skillset and the confidence<br />you need to successfully manage crucial conversations and ensure that both<br />sides have the best chance of leaving the encounter feeling happy.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p> Define &amp; detect a Crucial Conversation<br /> Assess your usual approach to stress<br /> Recognize the power of Dialogue<br /> Recognize personal dialogue patterns &amp; change it into positive stories<br /> Use S.T.A.T.E &amp; AAMP techniques to tell your story &amp; learn the path of<br />others<br /> Handle disagreements effectively using the ABC Method<br /> Describe and practice methods to move from conversation to actions and<br />results</p>', NULL, 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(70, 'Data Analysis & Reporting Techniques Using Excel', 280, '2022-03-02', '2022-03-30', '11:00:00', '15:00:00', 10, 'images/courses/1644293977.png', 14, 0, '2022-02-08 04:19:38', '2022-02-08 04:19:38', '<p>Overview<br />&bull; It is no surprise for corporate staff to be staff to be overwhelmed by the<br />abundance of instructed data.</p>\r\n<p>&bull; ERPs and database have evolved to a point where they can house<br />amazingly large amounts of data the question now is, what do you do<br />with this data to add value .</p>\r\n<p>&bull; this workshop will introduce business intelligence (BI), hands on, to<br />allow you to clean, normalize, interpret, analyze and report large volumes<br />of data. you will be able to establish historical relationships, analyze the<br />current situation and predict future strategies</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Design detailed reports from multiple sets of data through a variety of sources.<br />&bull; Manipulate the data within your reports to suit your business needs.<br />&bull; Extract data from your reports to use in different functions and formulas.<br />&bull; Create an attractive chart and diagram for your business reports to help illustrate data<br />&bull; Learn the concepts of gathering, cleaning and storage of data.<br />&bull; Come up with multiple scenarios to resolve business problems within extracted data.<br />&bull; Design a data model for your large data groups.<br />&bull; Mine and uncover hidden information with DAX.<br />&bull; Use Power Queries and practice shaping, blending and exploring files in Excel`s.<br />query editor , and create completely automated loading procedures inside of Excel.<br />&bull; Use Power Pivot and DAX to explore and analyze our Excel data model.</p>', NULL, 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(71, 'Power BI Reports & Interactive Dashboards', 280, '2022-02-06', '2022-02-17', '11:00:00', '15:00:00', 10, 'images/courses/1644294265.png', 14, 0, '2022-02-08 04:24:26', '2022-02-08 04:24:26', '<p>Overview :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; In this workshop you will be able to turn your data into<br />powerful intelligence and insight to drive your business<br />decisions. Power BI uses powerful drag and drop<br />capabilities that make it a breeze to create reports and<br />dashboard.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes : &bull; Introduction to Power BI and how to signup<br />&bull; How to create your first online report and dashboard<br />&bull; How to download the Power BI Desktop Designer<br />&bull; Loading, transforming and filtering data in Power BI<br />&bull; Creating tables and reports<br />&bull; Using filters and slicers<br />&bull; Learning how to use the wide range of graphs and<br />visualizations<br />&bull; Creating relationships between tables of data<br />&bull; Creating powerful calculations, key metrics and key<br />performance indicators<br />&bull; Creating interactive dashboards<br />&bull; Publishing dashboards to Power BI</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(72, 'Public Speaking : Complexly to Simplicity  ( By SPS )', 600, '2022-03-06', '2022-02-17', '13:00:00', '16:00:00', 10, 'images/courses/1644294427.png', 9, 0, '2022-02-28 09:46:10', '2022-02-08 04:27:08', '<p>PROGRAM OVERVIEW<br />◘ Complexity is one of the biggest barriers to communication when it comes to<br />communicate a complex technical message to non-technical audience, it is the<br />curse of knowledge.<br />◘ This journey begins with you, adapting a &ldquo;You attitude&rdquo; &ldquo;audience centric<br />approach&rdquo; in communicating the complex information, which put the<br />audience first when creating a message to be more accessible to them, the<br />Program will help you adapting this approach.<br />◘ The Program will introduce you to techniques and tools to avoid making<br />assumptions of your audience and start thinking differently, from their<br />perspective, analyze them to predict how are you going to tailor the<br />appropriate simple message.<br />◘ The Program will help you with a set of practical techniques to switch your<br />mindset and your usual thinking pattern as a technical expert to be able to<br />translate and chunk complex technical information into simple<br />comprehensible language to bridge the gap between tech and non-tech<br />stakeholders in your organization.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', NULL, 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(73, 'Coaching Skills', 430, '2022-03-20', '2022-03-23', '13:00:00', '16:00:00', 10, 'images/courses/1644294752.png', 12, 0, '2022-02-08 04:32:32', '2022-02-08 04:32:32', '<p>Overview<br />Coach, Mentor, Role Model, Supporter, Guide... do these words ring a bell?<br />Being a coach involves being able to draw from several disciplines. Coaching is<br />based on a partnership that involves giving both support and challenging<br />opportunities to employees. Mentorship is a related skill that is often a part of<br />coaching. It&rsquo;s about being a guide, offering wisdom and advice when it is<br />needed.<br />This highly interactive workshop is designed with a purpose to provide the<br />learners with keys on how and when to coach (and when to use other tools, like<br />mentoring) is an essential skill that can benefit both; the learner and the<br />organization.</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Understand how coaching can be used to develop your team.<br />&bull; Develop the coaching and mentoring skills that help improve individual<br />&bull; performance.<br />&bull; Demonstrate the behaviors and practices of an effective coach.<br />&bull; Recognize employees&rsquo; strengths and give them the feedback they need to<br />succeed.<br />&bull; Identify employee problems and ways you can help to correct them.</p>', NULL, 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(74, 'Sales Planning & Forecasting', 430, '2022-03-27', '2022-03-30', '13:00:00', '16:00:00', 10, 'images/courses/1644849712.png', 16, 0, '2022-02-28 09:43:56', '2022-02-08 04:36:22', '<p>Overview<br />&bull; This is a sales planning and forecasting workshop that<br />covers both qualitative and basic quantitative aspects such<br />as the planning process and forecasting techniques. This<br />workshop aims to help the sales professionals better<br />understand the planning process and use better forecasting<br />techniques for existing as well as new products.<br />&bull; It focuses on improving organization and forecasting skills,<br />as well as other technical competencies aimed at guiding<br />salespeople towards higher performance.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Demonstrate traits of an excellent sales manager facing modern<br />market challenges<br />&bull; Design and deliver sales strategies, organize sales territories,<br />and use different forecasting models to optimize sales results<br />&bull; Know Planning function and process best practices<br />&bull; Know Techniques of organizing Sales Force</p>', NULL, 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(75, 'Business Agility', 600, '2022-03-20', '2022-03-23', '18:00:00', '21:00:00', 10, 'images/courses/1644295180.png', 11, 0, '2022-02-08 04:39:40', '2022-02-08 04:39:40', '<p>Overview<br />The shortest and briefest definition of Agility is the inherent ability to respond to<br />change. But does that mean in Business World?<br />Can you think of a company that has gone bust? Nokia, Kodak? You&rsquo;ve probably heard<br />of more examples, there are loads of them out there! Big names like these have failed<br />to cope with the rapid changes and therefore were doomed to fail.<br />Now, more than ever before, organizations need to reinvent themselves to cope with<br />the ever-changing nature of the workplace.<br />This highly interactive workshop is designed to raise the participants&rsquo; awareness of<br />Business Agility &amp; it&rsquo;s best practices. The learning process is based on real-world<br />business cases like McDonalds, Panadol, Mazda, Apple, Harley Davidson &amp; more.<br />Participants will also acquire the knowledge &amp; tools needed to create an action plan to<br />meet ambiguity with agility in order implement new approaches such as Business<br />Model Canvas &amp; Blue Ocean Strategy that transforms an undesired situation into an<br />opportunity.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Recognize the importance of leading agile and resilient organizations during<br />turbulent times<br />&bull; Make decisions in chaotic situations<br />&bull; Use problem solving tools to provide effective solutions<br />&bull; Identify ambiguity in business and adapt it to agility<br />&bull; Lead and develop proactive mechanisms to withstand environmental<br />disruptions<br />&bull; Create compelling strategies to lead and drive agility and resilience<br />&bull; Use Business Model Canvas &amp; Blue Ocean Strategy to create value<br />&bull; Demonstrate agile leadership skills in the modern world</p>', NULL, 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(76, 'Writing Proposals & Reports', 430, '2022-03-27', '2022-03-30', '18:00:00', '21:00:00', 10, 'images/courses/1644295330.png', 13, 0, '2022-02-08 04:42:10', '2022-02-08 04:42:10', '<p>Overview<br />It is essential to understand how to write reports and proposals that get read. We<br />write reports in a range of formats and a variety of purposes. Whether you need<br />to report on a product analysis, inventory, feasibility studies, or something else,<br />report writing is a skill you will use again and again.<br />Having a method to prepare these documents will help you be as efficient as<br />possible with the task. This highly interactive workshop will build on a solid base<br />of writing skills to present information in formal, informal, and proposal styles.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Prepare Reports And Proposals That Inform, Persuade, and Provide<br />Information.<br />&bull; Review Your Work So That It Is Clear, Concise, Complete, and Correct.<br />&bull; Apply Business Writing Skills in Real Work Applications<br />&bull; Employ The Best Approach For Winning a Proposal<br />&bull; Describe &amp; Follow The Four Stages of Writing A Report<br />&bull; Create a Winning Design that Gets Responses</p>', NULL, 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(77, 'Successful Planning , Organizing and Control', 2500, '2022-06-01', '2022-06-02', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1646041311.png', 11, 0, '2022-02-28 09:41:52', '2022-02-12 15:43:01', '<p>Overview<br />The primary challenge faced by organizations and managers today is to<br />creatively solve business problems. The principles of management have been<br />categorized into the four major functions of planning, organizing, leading, and<br />controlling popularly known as the P-O-L-C framework; Planning, Organizing,<br />Leading &amp; Controlling.<br />The highly interactive workshop focuses closely at 3 elements of the P.O.L.C<br />Framework, which are; Planning, Organizing &amp; Controlling. It provide a step by<br />step guide to plan for a project that gets results. It is designed to equip the<br />participants with the essential skills needed to fulfill their responsibilities in a<br />professional way. The concepts, methods and techniques presented include both<br />well established and latest thinking to provide the essential knowledge, skills,<br />and toolkit to ensure more successful outcomes.</p>\r\n<p>The Learning Outcomes :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Apply a professional, systematic approach to planning and employing the<br />\'SMART\' criteria to objectives setting<br />&bull; Produce realistic plans, determine the critical path, and manage risks<br />&bull; Use environmental scanning, budgeting, and breakeven analysis as tools for<br />planning and forecasting<br />&bull; Define planning tools &amp; techniques such as \'Gantt\' charts and \'Load\' charts<br />&bull; Recognize the importance of control, and of properly utilizing key<br />performance measures to keep work on track<br />&bull; Mobilize resources, accurately monitor project performance, and maintain<br />control of the project<br />&bull; Assess the impact of organizational change and manage people\'s resistance<br />to change&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Dates : 01 &amp; 02 June&nbsp; 2022</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(78, 'Excel Core ( From Basic to Advanced )', 2200, '2022-06-04', '2022-02-07', '10:00:00', '15:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1644681240.png', 14, 0, '2022-06-07 11:26:26', '2022-02-12 15:54:01', '<p>Overview<br />Excel tools enable us to be more productive and<br />efficient By attending participants will learn to leverage<br />the powerful features of Excel from basic to advanced<br />covering Calculation, Formatting, Analysis and<br />Reporting</p>\r\n<p>The learning Outcomes :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Reviewing the basics of Formatting and Calculation tools<br />&bull; Mastering Excel most important functions<br />&bull; Analyzing Data and Alternative data sets<br />&bull; Apply the key Excel functions to prepare data for analysis<br />&bull; Apply advanced calculations<br />&bull; Create and customize pivot tables to reconcile and analyze accounts efficiently<br />&bull; Utilize pivot tables functions and calculations to generate a set of management and<br />business analysis reports<br />&bull; Creating Advanced charts and graphics<br />&bull; Changing workbook Appearance</p>', '<p>Dates : 04,11,18,25 June &amp; 02 July 2022&nbsp;</p>', 'Virtual', 'eg', 0),
(79, 'Power BI Reports & Interactive Dashboards', 2700, '2022-06-04', '2022-06-25', '16:00:00', '21:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1644682209.png', 14, 0, '2022-05-10 13:02:15', '2022-02-12 16:10:10', '<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Overview :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&bull; In this workshop you will be able to turn your data into<br />powerful intelligence and insight to drive your business<br />decisions. Power BI uses powerful drag and drop<br />capabilities that make it a breeze to create reports and<br />dashboard.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The Learning Outcomes :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&bull; Introduction to Power BI and how to signup<br />&bull; How to create your first online report and dashboard<br />&bull; How to download the Power BI Desktop Designer<br />&bull; Loading, transforming and filtering data in Power BI<br />&bull; Creating tables and reports<br />&bull; Using filters and slicers<br />&bull; Learning how to use the wide range of graphs and<br />visualizations<br />&bull; Creating relationships between tables of data<br />&bull; Creating powerful calculations, key metrics and key<br />performance indicators<br />&bull; Creating interactive dashboards<br />&bull; Publishing dashboards to Power BI</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong> 01012769079&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 04,11,18 &amp; 25 June 2022&nbsp;</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(80, 'Your First 90 Days as a Manager', 4500, '2022-02-06', '2022-04-06', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1644682299.png', 12, 0, '2022-02-21 04:20:28', '2022-02-12 16:11:39', '<p>Overview<br />&bull; As long as there have been leaders, there have been leadership transitions.<br />The changes challenges these transitions impose on the new leader are as<br />old as human society. Those challenges have not gotten any easier. On the<br />contrary, the complexity of modern organizations and the speed at which<br />business gets conducted have seemingly added to it. This highly interactive<br />workshop is your roadmap for taking charge in your first 90 days in your new<br />position as a newly promoted manager. Why do you need it? Because<br />transitions are critical times when small differences in your actions can have<br />huge impacts on results.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Describe &amp; develop new leadership competencies<br />&bull; Conduct a personal SWOT assessment to expand on the strengths &amp;<br />improve the weaknesses<br />&bull; Follow a 90-days action plan overcome the promotion challenge<br />&bull; Use the ADEPT Model to place people in the right roles &amp; provide the<br />right support<br />&bull; Define Decision-making styles &amp; employ each style according to the<br />situation</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates&nbsp; : 02,03 &amp; 04 June 2022&nbsp;</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(81, 'The Leadership Mastery', 4200, '2022-06-05', '2022-06-08', '10:00:00', '14:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1646040993.png', 12, 0, '2022-02-28 09:36:33', '2022-02-12 16:35:30', '<p>Overview<br />&bull; The workshop addresses the perennial differences between management<br />and leadership. It aims at providing participants with an overview of how to be<br />a successful leader, You will get the opportunity to discover your hidden<br />talents and practice what you learn before going back to your workplace and<br />influence people, events and your own future as a Leader</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Distinguish between management and leadership<br />&bull; Identify their strengths and leadership styles through self-assessments<br />&bull; Apply breakthrough leadership and communication techniques to drive<br />business value and become a more powerful leader<br />&bull; Implement best practices for influencing peers, managers, subordinates,<br />customers and other stakeholders<br />&bull; Explain how to effectively handle challenges such as delivering unpopular<br />news, increasing team motivation and winning hearts and minds<br />&bull; Deliver powerful messages that lead to rapid action and that control<br />emotions when facing resistance and conflict<br />&bull; Optimize internal communication and sell their organization&rsquo;s vision,<br />mission and values to their team members</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Date : 05,06,07 &amp; 08 June 2022&nbsp;</p>', 'Virtual', 'eg', 0),
(82, 'Dynamic Presentations (BY SPS)', 4200, '2022-06-05', '2022-06-16', '12:00:00', '15:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645531584.png', 9, 0, '2022-02-22 12:06:24', '2022-02-12 16:46:07', '<p>Overview :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>◘ As an expert in the information you&rsquo;re presenting, you have to find a way to<br />support your message in an entertaining way.</p>\r\n<p>◘ Either you are presenting data you received via reports, dashboards, and<br />systems to your peers or the top management to help them taking a decision<br />or to find a solution Or presenting a new process or a strategic plan for your<br />team ,so that employees understand how their work contributes to the overall<br />strategy.</p>\r\n<p>◘ Dynamic presentation program will help you switch the boring rigid static<br />presentation into an interesting highly engaging dynamic one, to have the<br />advantage of perfectly responsive design for your information and your<br />presentation will go much smoother. Not only will your audience be<br />impressed, but they are going to even be pulled in by your message.</p>\r\n<p>◘ In this program you will be introduced to a set of techniques and tools for the<br />transformation of raw data into meaningful ,useful information in an<br />interesting dynamic highly engaging way.</p>\r\n<p>◘ You will learn How to display data the right way in your Presentations A<br />Context plays a huge role in how best to render data by first asking yourself &ldquo;<br />Am I Presenting Or Circulating My Data?&rdquo; &ldquo;What Message Am I Trying To<br />Convey? &ldquo;</p>\r\n<p>◘ This program will help you presenting your personal brand by mastering the<br />way you are presenting .presenting your points with power, not just<br />PowerPoint</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &n