(87, 'Advanced Sales Professional', 3500, '2022-06-10', '2022-06-24', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1644686846.png', 16, 0, '2022-02-21 04:20:28', '2022-02-12 17:27:27', '<p>Overview<br />&bull; This Workshop provides participants with core knowledge about sales as a<br />function and as a process; this means that participants will get solid exposure<br />to sales and its contribution to company growth.<br />&bull; In addition, participants will acquire several skills related to negotiating deals,<br />overcoming obstacles, resolving customer issues and closing sales.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :</p>\r\n<p>● Identify and adopt the right professional selling behaviors and skills<br />needed to maximize sales performance<br />● Develop critical self-driven practices to optimize personal and<br />business effectiveness and efficiency<br />● Master and implement the sales process to successfully handle<br />objections and close more deals<br />● Manage customer expectations and exceed it to gain customer<br />loyalty and generate repeat business<br />● Master the art of verbal and non-verbal communication to create<br />an atmosphere of respect and trust in the seller-buyer interface</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Date : 10,17 &amp; 24 June 2022</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(88, 'Negotiation Keys for Master Negation', 2800, '2022-06-12', '2022-06-13', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1644686890.png', 9, 0, '2022-02-21 04:20:28', '2022-02-12 17:28:10', '<p>Overview</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Everyone has to negotiate at some point in his or her<br />life. This highly interactive workshop is designed to<br />provide experienced negotiators who aspire to become<br />master negotiators with the advanced tools needed to<br />take their negotiation skills to the next level.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Identify different negotiation models &amp; styles &amp; when to use each<br />&bull; Assess personal points of strength &amp; weakness in negotiation as<br />well as those of the counterpart to optimize negotiation<br />outcomes<br />&bull; Apply tactics in different negotiation scenarios<br />&bull; Using a set of effective skills for better negotiation outcomes<br />&bull; Demonstrate advanced skills in commercial &amp; Sales Negotiation<br />&bull; Modify negotiation plans as well as create plan B for deadlock<br />negotiations</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 12 &amp; 13 June 2022</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(89, 'Design Thinking - Unlock Innovation', 2800, '2022-06-15', '2022-06-16', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1646040323.png', 9, 0, '2022-02-28 09:25:24', '2022-02-12 17:39:19', '<p>Overview<br />Design thinking is a powerful process of problem solving, a journey that begins<br />with having an empathic understanding of unmet customer needs. From that<br />insight emerges a blend of Heart, Head and Hand process that is based on<br />vision,<br />continuing on to development, applied creativity, prototyping then diving into<br />experimentation, practical creation &amp;amp; testing. This highly interactive<br />workshop is<br />designed to help the participants learn a proven, systematic approach to new<br />product development through a process that puts unmet customer needs at the<br />center of the problem. It also helps them apply design thinking approaches to<br />business, so that the success rate for innovation can improve substantially.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Use Design Thinking to solve problems more creatively<br />&bull; Understand problems from the customers perspective<br />&bull; Apply different brainstorming techniques to identify innovative ideas<br />&bull; Use effective design research<br />&bull; Understand the value of creating prototypes to test your ideas<br />&bull; Keep your design ideas moving forward</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates :&nbsp; 15 &amp; 16 June 2022&nbsp;</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(90, 'Warehouse Operations', 2500, '2022-06-19', '2022-06-20', '10:00:00', '17:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1646040280.png', 18, 0, '2022-02-28 09:24:40', '2022-02-12 19:09:49', '<p>Overview<br />&bull; This workshop is aiming the employees of (Warehouse,<br />stock control, planning, and supply chain) who need an<br />overview of the key skills and drivers involved when<br />viewing warehouse from a value chain point of view. It<br />examines what warehouse &amp; inventory management is<br />fundamentally about. It will also explore how to change<br />current methods and activities so that benefits are<br />obtained.</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Throughout the workshop the Rules for Effective<br />warehouse &amp; inventory Management are identified and<br />discussed.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Explain the challenges, objectives and functions of warehousing<br />&bull; Identify the different types of storage and material handling systems<br />&bull; Develop key performance indicators and benchmark warehouse performance<br />&bull; Outline the cost and revenue aspects of warehousing<br />&bull; Improve supervisory skills and deal more effectively with warehouse stuff issues</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 19 &amp; 20 June 2022&nbsp;</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(91, 'Unlock Team Synergy', 2500, '2022-06-22', '2022-06-23', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1644693242.png', 9, 0, '2022-02-21 04:20:28', '2022-02-12 19:14:03', '<p>Overview<br />&bull; &ldquo;No one can whistle a symphony. It takes an orchestra to play it.&rdquo;<br />Being part of a team that gets results begins with establishing a team mindset for<br />yourself as team member. For that reason, this highly interactive workshop<br />begins with a discussion of what a team is and the essential nature of the team<br />mindset.<br />&bull; From there, the workshop journey will lead you through the foundational skills<br />that make teams work, including communication &amp;amp; essential conflict<br />resolution skills to work out unique team challenges &amp;amp; resolve potential<br />conflicts among the team members..</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Describe the Characteristics of High Performing Teams<br />&bull; Understand the importance of playing to different strengths and skills<br />&bull; Recognize the need for clear and effective communication<br />&bull; Understand the challenges of conflict resolution within teams<br />&bull; Participate in enhancing team&rsquo;s collaboration</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 22 &amp; 23 June 2022&nbsp;</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(92, 'Writing Like Pro', 2800, '2022-06-26', '2022-06-27', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1646039987.png', 13, 0, '2022-02-28 09:19:48', '2022-02-12 19:20:26', '<p>Overview<br />&bull; The clearer &amp; more concise a message is, the more likely it can resolve a<br />complex situation.<br />&bull; This workshop is designed to provide learners with advanced key business<br />writing tools for better &amp; more powerful impact.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Recognize the importance of setting an objective that<br />compliments the purpose of your writing<br />&bull; Apply the essential tools for effective business writing<br />&bull; Develop a personal writing style<br />&bull; Design a written document &amp; demonstrate the value of visual<br />aids &amp; style<br />&bull; Apply proofreading skills to ensure accuracy<br />&bull; Identify a challenging situation &amp; respond to it accordingly</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 26 &amp; 27 June 2022&nbsp;</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(93, 'Retail Selling', 2500, '2022-06-29', '2022-06-30', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1646039953.png', 16, 0, '2022-02-28 09:19:13', '2022-02-12 19:23:23', '<p>Overview :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Overview<br />&bull; During the training you&rsquo;ll cover what it takes to make a sale from<br />understanding the sales process and generating business through to how to<br />handle objections and ask for the order.<br />&bull; This training will provide your sales teams with the latest thinking in retail<br />sales.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Learn How to Project the right image<br />&bull; Open and maintain a conversation, with confidence<br />&bull; Discover customer needs<br />&bull; Match customer needs with potentially relevant products or<br />services<br />&bull; Structure and control conversations to reach a successful outcome</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 29 &amp; 30 June 2022&nbsp;</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(94, 'Effective Delegation', 1600, '2022-06-29', '2022-06-30', '12:00:00', '15:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1644694238.png', 12, 0, '2022-03-22 13:11:51', '2022-02-12 19:30:39', '<p>Overview<br />Effective delegation is one of the most valuable skills you can master. It reduces<br />your workload and develops employee skills. Delegating prepares employees<br />who work for you to be able to handle your responsibilities and simultaneously<br />allows you to advance to other career opportunities within your organization.<br />Delegation is often one of the hardest skills for a manager to master. However,<br />the skill can be learned. This interactive one-day workshop will explore many of<br />the facets of delegation, including when to delegate and to whom to delegate.<br />We will also go through the delegation process step by step and learn about<br />techniques to overcome problems</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Identify how delegation fits into your job and how it can make you more<br />&bull; successful<br />&bull; Identify different ways of delegating tasks<br />&bull; Use an effective process for effective delegation<br />&bull; Give better instructions for better delegation results<br />&bull; Recognize common delegation pitfalls and how to avoid them<br />&bull; Monitor delegation results<br />&bull; Give effective feedback</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 29 &amp; 30 June 2022</p>', 'Virtual', 'eg', 0);
