(95, 'Excel Core ( From Basic to Advanced )', 250, '2022-06-04', '2022-07-02', '11:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1644695078.png', 14, 0, '2022-02-12 19:44:39', '2022-02-12 19:44:39', '<p>Overview<br />Excel tools enable us to be more productive and<br />efficient By attending participants will learn to leverage<br />the powerful features of Excel from basic to advanced<br />covering Calculation, Formatting, Analysis and<br />Reporting</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Reviewing the basics of Formatting and Calculation tools<br />&bull; Mastering Excel most important functions<br />&bull; Analyzing Data and Alternative data sets<br />&bull; Apply the key Excel functions to prepare data for analysis<br />&bull; Apply advanced calculations<br />&bull; Create and customize pivot tables to reconcile and analyze accounts efficiently<br />&bull; Utilize pivot tables functions and calculations to generate a set of management and<br />business analysis reports<br />&bull; Creating Advanced charts and graphics<br />&bull; Changing workbook Appearance</p>', '<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Dates : 04,11,18,25 June &amp; 02 July</p>', 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(96, 'The Leadership Mastery', 500, '2022-06-05', '2022-06-08', '11:00:00', '15:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1646037439.png', 12, 0, '2022-02-28 08:37:20', '2022-02-12 19:50:51', '<p>&nbsp;The workshop addresses the perennial differences between management<br />and leadership. It aims at providing participants with an overview of how to be<br />a successful leader, You will get the opportunity to discover your hidden<br />talents and practice what you learn before going back to your workplace and<br />influence people, events and your own future as a Leader</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Distinguish between management and leadership<br />&bull; Identify their strengths and leadership styles through self-assessments<br />&bull; Apply breakthrough leadership and communication techniques to drive<br />business value and become a more powerful leader<br />&bull; Implement best practices for influencing peers, managers, subordinates,<br />customers and other stakeholders<br />&bull; Explain how to effectively handle challenges such as delivering unpopular<br />news, increasing team motivation and winning hearts and minds<br />&bull; Deliver powerful messages that lead to rapid action and that control<br />emotions when facing resistance and conflict<br />&bull; Optimize internal communication and sell their organization&rsquo;s vision,<br />mission and values to their team members</p>', '<p>Dates : 05,06 , 07 &amp; 08&nbsp; June 2022</p>', 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(97, 'Dynamic Presentations  ( By SPS )', 600, '2022-06-05', '2022-06-16', '13:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1646037252.png', 9, 0, '2022-02-28 08:34:12', '2022-02-12 20:01:26', '<p>Overview :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>◘ As an expert in the information you&rsquo;re presenting, you have to find a way to<br />support your message in an entertaining way.</p>\r\n<p>◘ Either you are presenting data you received via reports, dashboards, and<br />systems to your peers or the top management to help them taking a decision<br />or to find a solution Or presenting a new process or a strategic plan for your<br />team ,so that employees understand how their work contributes to the overall<br />strategy.</p>\r\n<p>◘ Dynamic presentation program will help you switch the boring rigid static<br />presentation into an interesting highly engaging dynamic one, to have the<br />advantage of perfectly responsive design for your information and your<br />presentation will go much smoother. Not only will your audience be<br />impressed, but they are going to even be pulled in by your message.</p>\r\n<p>◘ In this program you will be introduced to a set of techniques and tools for the<br />transformation of raw data into meaningful ,useful information in an<br />interesting dynamic highly engaging way.</p>\r\n<p>◘ You will learn How to display data the right way in your Presentations A<br />Context plays a huge role in how best to render data by first asking yourself &ldquo;<br />Am I Presenting Or Circulating My Data?&rdquo; &ldquo;What Message Am I Trying To<br />Convey? &ldquo;</p>\r\n<p>◘ This program will help you presenting your personal brand by mastering the<br />way you are presenting .presenting your points with power, not just<br />PowerPoint</p>', '<p>Dates : &nbsp;05,07,09,12,14 &amp; 16 June 2022&nbsp;</p>', 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(98, 'Financial Analysis & Reporting', 430, '2022-06-06', '2022-06-08', '11:00:00', '15:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1644696457.jpeg', 17, 0, '2022-02-12 20:07:38', '2022-02-12 20:07:38', '<p>&bull; This workshop takes you from the first step of<br />understanding the relationships between the different<br />elements of financial statements, through calculating<br />and analyzing the financial ratios to the last step of<br />presenting recommendations.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Apply the framework of financial statements analysis<br />&bull; Use ratio and financial analysis<br />&bull; Interpret company financials and industry position<br />&bull; Appraise the process of company evaluation and analysis<br />&bull; Analyze real-life financial statements from companies<br />traded on the world stock exchanges<br />&bull; Prepare financial analysis template models</p>', '<p>Dates : 06,07 &amp; 08 June 2022&nbsp;</p>', 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(99, 'Design Thinking - Unlock Innovation', 500, '2022-06-26', '2022-06-28', '10:00:00', '14:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1646037071.png', 9, 0, '2022-02-28 08:31:11', '2022-02-12 20:14:59', '<p>Design thinking is a powerful process of problem solving, a journey that begins<br />with having an empathic understanding of unmet customer needs. From that<br />insight emerges a blend of Heart, Head and Hand process that is based on<br />vision,<br />continuing on to development, applied creativity, prototyping then diving into<br />experimentation, practical creation &amp;amp; testing. This highly interactive<br />workshop is<br />designed to help the participants learn a proven, systematic approach to new<br />product development through a process that puts unmet customer needs at the<br />center of the problem. It also helps them apply design thinking approaches to<br />business, so that the success rate for innovation can improve substantially.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Use Design Thinking to solve problems more creatively<br />&bull; Understand problems from the customers perspective<br />&bull; Apply different brainstorming techniques to identify innovative ideas<br />&bull; Use effective design research<br />&bull; Understand the value of creating prototypes to test your ideas<br />&bull; Keep your design ideas moving forward</p>', '<p>Dates : 26,27 &amp; 28 June 2022</p>', 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(100, 'Effective Delegation', 200, '2022-06-29', '2022-06-30', '13:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1644697457.png', 12, 0, '2022-02-28 08:58:33', '2022-02-12 20:24:17', '<p>Effective delegation is one of the most valuable skills you can master. It reduces<br />your workload and develops employee skills. Delegating prepares employees<br />who work for you to be able to handle your responsibilities and simultaneously<br />allows you to advance to other career opportunities within your organization.<br />Delegation is often one of the hardest skills for a manager to master. However,<br />the skill can be learned. This interactive one-day workshop will explore many of<br />the facets of delegation, including when to delegate and to whom to delegate.<br />We will also go through the delegation process step by step and learn about<br />techniques to overcome problems</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Identify how delegation fits into your job and how it can make you more<br />&bull; successful<br />&bull; Identify different ways of delegating tasks<br />&bull; Use an effective process for effective delegation<br />&bull; Give better instructions for better delegation results<br />&bull; Recognize common delegation pitfalls and how to avoid them<br />&bull; Monitor delegation results<br />&bull; Give effective feedback</p>', '<p>Dates : 29 &amp; 30 June 2022</p>', 'Classroom', 'sa', 0),
(101, 'Principles of Successful Negotiations', 400, '2022-06-19', '2022-06-21', '10:00:00', '14:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1653992107.jpg', 9, 0, '2022-05-31 10:42:07', '2022-02-12 20:31:32', '<p>&bull; Everyone has to negotiate at some point in his or her<br />life. This highly interactive workshop is designed to<br />provide experienced negotiators who aspire to become<br />master negotiators with the advanced tools needed to<br />take their negotiation skills to the next level.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Identify different negotiation models &amp; styles &amp; when to use each<br />&bull; Assess personal points of strength &amp; weakness in negotiation as<br />well as those of the counterpart to optimize negotiation<br />outcomes<br />&bull; Apply tactics in different negotiation scenarios<br />&bull; Using a set of effective skills for better negotiation outcomes<br />&bull; Demonstrate advanced skills in commercial &amp; Sales Negotiation<br />&bull; Modify negotiation plans as well as create plan B for deadlock<br />negotiations</p>', '<p>Dates : 19,20 &amp; 21 June 2022</p>', 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(102, 'Crisis Management & Business Continuity', 3300, '2022-04-03', '2022-04-17', '10:00:00', '13:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1646036424.png', 10, 0, '2022-02-28 08:20:24', '2022-02-13 11:05:31', NULL, '<p>03,05,10 ,12 &amp; 17 April&nbsp;</p>', 'Virtual', 'eg', 0),
(103, 'Building High Performance Team', 4200, '2022-04-03', '2022-04-10', '10:00:00', '13:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645975711.png', 12, 0, '2022-02-27 15:28:31', '2022-02-13 19:01:16', '<p>Success as a manager is heavily influenced by how well your team operates and<br />what kind of results they achieve. Is your team able to solve problems? Can they<br />resolve conflict? Are they enthusiastic and motivated to do their best? Do they<br />work well together? This highly interactive three-day workshop is designed for<br />participants who want to develop their team leadership skills and unleash the<br />talent of their individual team members.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Identify different types of teams.<br />&bull; Build teamwork by recognizing and tapping into the characteristics of an<br />effective team.<br />&bull; Promote trust and rapport by exploring your team player style and how it<br />impacts group dynamics.<br />&bull; Recognize the key elements that move a team from involvement to<br />empowerment and how to give these elements to your team.<br />&bull; Develop strategies for dealing with team conflict and common problems.<br />&bull; Understand how action planning and analysis tools can help your team<br />perform better.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 03,04,05,06, 07 &amp; 10 April 2022</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Virtual', 'eg', 0),
(104, 'Personnel & Labor law', 2200, '2022-04-04', '2022-04-07', '10:00:00', '13:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1644779851.png', 19, 0, '2022-02-13 19:17:32', '2022-02-13 19:17:32', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 04,05, 06 &amp; 07 April 2022</p>', 'Virtual', 'eg', 0),
(105, 'Excel Master - Advanced Level', 1600, '2022-04-08', '2022-04-22', '14:00:00', '17:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1644779970.jpg', 14, 0, '2022-02-21 04:20:28', '2022-02-13 19:19:30', '<p>&bull; This Workshop is designed to focus on the advanced Excel tools And features that goes beyond the basics and enable users to go from only editing and formatting sheets to creating their own Advanced calculations and reports instead of working one Previously prepared ones &bull; Also you will check in this workshop the different powerful tools that make you the Master of Excel</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Mastering Excel most important functions</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Analyzing Data and Alternative data sets</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Apply the key Excel functions to prepare data for analysis</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Apply advanced calculations</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Create and customize pivot tables to reconcile and analyze accounts efficiently</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Utilize pivot tables functions and calculations to generate a set of management and business analysis reports</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Creating Advanced charts and graphics</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Changing workbook Appearance</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 08,09,15,16 &amp; 22 April 2022&nbsp;</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(106, 'Handling Customer Complains', 2200, '2022-04-10', '2022-04-21', '10:00:00', '13:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645975540.png', 15, 0, '2022-02-27 15:25:40', '2022-02-13 19:26:17', '<p>Handling difficult customers can be a challenging task especially if it is<br />charged with irrational emotion. Often, the natural reaction would be to feel<br />defensive and try explaining why the situation occurred. More often than not,<br />this kind of reaction only make the situation go worse. This workshop is<br />designed to help the participants get into of their customers, understand their<br />pain and expectation, understand their preferences &amp; priorities, in order to<br />deliver a service that exceeds their expectations and fulfill both their<br />materialistic &amp; emotional needs.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :</p>\r\n<p>&bull;Define customer service and how to use this understanding to CS in handling<br />customers<br />&bull;Use the RATER Framework to enhance the Customers experience<br />&bull;Develop a Customer Journey Map<br />&bull;Describe the essential skillset for CS<br />&bull;Identify the four types of customers and how to handle each effectively</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 10,12,17, 19 &amp; 21 April 2022</p>', 'Virtual', 'eg', 0),
(107, 'Business Agility', 4200, '2022-04-10', '2022-04-21', '10:00:00', '13:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1644780848.png', 11, 0, '2022-02-25 18:56:39', '2022-02-13 19:34:08', '<p>The shortest and briefest definition of Agility is the inherent ability to respond to<br />change. But does that mean in Business World?<br />Can you think of a company that has gone bust? Nokia, Kodak? You&rsquo;ve probably heard<br />of more examples, there are loads of them out there! Big names like these have failed<br />to cope with the rapid changes and therefore were doomed to fail.<br />Now, more than ever before, organizations need to reinvent themselves to cope with<br />the ever-changing nature of the workplace.<br />This highly interactive workshop is designed to raise the participants&rsquo; awareness of<br />Business Agility &amp; it&rsquo;s best practices. The learning process is based on real-world<br />business cases like McDonalds, Panadol, Mazda, Apple, Harley Davidson &amp; more.<br />Participants will also acquire the knowledge &amp; tools needed to create an action plan to<br />meet ambiguity with agility in order implement new approaches such as Business<br />Model Canvas &amp; Blue Ocean Strategy that transforms an undesired situation into an<br />opportunity.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Recognize the importance of leading agile and resilient organizations during<br />turbulent times<br />&bull; Make decisions in chaotic situations<br />&bull; Use problem solving tools to provide effective solutions<br />&bull; Identify ambiguity in business and adapt it to agility<br />&bull; Lead and develop proactive mechanisms to withstand environmental<br />disruptions<br />&bull; Create compelling strategies to lead and drive agility and resilience<br />&bull; Use Business Model Canvas &amp; Blue Ocean Strategy to create value<br />&bull; Demonstrate agile leadership skills in the modern world</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 10,12,17, 19 &amp; 21 April 2022</p>', 'Virtual', 'eg', 0),
