(122, 'Excel Master - Advanced Level', 1800, '2022-05-07', '2022-05-21', '16:00:00', '21:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645172874.jpg', 14, 0, '2022-02-25 19:05:13', '2022-02-18 08:27:54', '<p>&bull; This Workshop is designed to focus on the advanced Excel tools And features that goes beyond the basics and enable users to go from only editing and formatting sheets to creating their own Advanced calculations and reports instead of working one Previously prepared ones &bull; Also you will check in this workshop the different powerful tools that make you the Master of Excel</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Mastering Excel most important functions</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Analyzing Data and Alternative data sets</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Apply the key Excel functions to prepare data for analysis</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Apply advanced calculations</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Create and customize pivot tables to reconcile and analyze accounts efficiently</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Utilize pivot tables functions and calculations to generate a set of management and business analysis reports</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Creating Advanced charts and graphics</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Changing workbook Appearance</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 07,14 &amp; 21 March 2022&nbsp;</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(123, 'Project Management', 5800, '2022-05-08', '2022-05-29', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645173111.png', 10, 0, '2022-02-21 04:20:28', '2022-02-18 08:31:51', '<p>&bull; The overall aim of this workshop is to provide participants with the necessary<br />skills required to plan their projects by creating project scope statements and<br />project work breakdown structures. Additionally, participants will learn how to<br />develop key performance indicators for monitoring and controlling their project<br />schedule and budget.<br />&bull; The workshop also aims at assisting participants in appraising the feasibility<br />of their projects by applying capital budgeting techniques. Finally, the<br />workshop will cover how to effectively plan project stakeholders&rsquo; engagement<br />and manage their expectations.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :</p>\r\n<p> Plan projects using statement of work and Work Breakdown Structure<br />(WBS)<br /> Schedule projects activities and build the project network model<br /> Calculate project budgets and schedule variances using Earned Value<br />(EV) Techniques<br /> Select the right projects using capital budgeting techniques<br /> Relate to project stakeholders through better negotiation and<br />communication skills</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 08,15,22 &amp; 29 May 2022</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(124, 'Your Business Writing Mojo !', 2500, '2022-05-08', '2022-05-11', '12:00:00', '15:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645173306.jpg', 13, 0, '2022-02-18 08:35:07', '2022-02-18 08:35:07', '<p>&bull; In business writing, the language is concrete, the point of view is clear,<br />and the points are well expressed.<br />&bull; This workshop is designed to provide the learners with a proven step-by-step<br />process, to write faster and more effectively.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Apply the basic tools of writing for effective outcome<br />&bull; Understand and master the punctuation &amp;amp; spelling techniques for<br />better Business writing<br />&bull; Develop a technical writing style<br />&bull; Identify the different types of writing<br />&bull; Avoid common mistakes in technical writing<br />&bull; Demonstrate an understanding of formal language required for business<br />communication</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates :08,09,10 &amp; 11 May 2022</p>', 'Virtual', 'eg', 0),
(125, 'Strategic Thinking & Planning', 3100, '2022-05-09', '2022-05-11', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645974704.png', 11, 0, '2022-02-27 15:11:45', '2022-02-18 12:03:34', '<p>&bull; In this workshop, we will cover the steps of the strategy management<br />process, starting with the \'thinking\' components of strategy, moving into the<br />\'planning\' components and ending with \'execution\',<br />&bull; Participants will be able to implement or improve the strategic process at their<br />organizations to reach their vision and achieve their mission.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :</p>\r\n<p>● Apply strategic thinking to analyze their current environment and<br />determine their organizational ambition<br />● Employ the strategic management process to best achieve the desired<br />ambition<br />● Assess and choose strategies that create a sustainable competitive<br />advantage for the organization<br />● Determine strategic objectives, Key Performance Indicators (KPIs)<br />and \'SMART\' targets for the organization<br />● Convert strategic plans to operating plans through creating strategic<br />initiatives and sequencing activities</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Dates : 09,10 &amp; 11 May 2022</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(126, 'Customer Service Professional', 2200, '2022-05-09', '2022-05-18', '18:00:00', '21:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645188743.png', 15, 0, '2022-03-22 13:03:27', '2022-02-18 12:52:24', '<p>While many organizations promise to deliver an incredible customer experience,<br />some are better at supplying this than others. This two-day interactive workshop<br />is designed around six critical elements of customer service that, when a<br />company truly embraces them, bring customers back to experience service that<br />outdoes the competition.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Define customer service and its approach<br />&bull; Understand how your own behavior affects the behavior of others<br />&bull; Demonstrate confidence and skill as a problem solver<br />&bull; Apply techniques to deal with difficult customers<br />&bull; Know how to provide excellent customer service</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 09,11,16 &amp; 18 May 2022</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0);
