(127, 'Public Speaking : Express to Impress (BY SPS)', 4500, '2022-05-13', '2022-05-27', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645189861.png', 9, 0, '2022-02-21 04:20:28', '2022-02-18 13:11:01', '<p>◘ As young professional seeking excellence in your professional world, public<br />speaking is a vital skill to your success and your business as well. You won&rsquo;t be<br />concerned anymore about how to overcome challenges in presenting yourself<br />and your ideas in different situations.<br />◘ Whether it&rsquo;s a meeting with your managers and co-workers or communicating<br />with other departments and customers on behalf of your entity. And because<br />Such situations require a powerful set of skills to be able to express and<br />impress!<br />◘ In our program, we will help you gaining all these required skills which will<br />positively impact all other elements of your professional development journey<br />to establish yourself as a valuable member in your organization.<br />◘ You will gain more confidence in yourself by mastering your verbal and<br />nonverbal communication aspects, asking the right questions to understand<br />and validate the received information.<br />◘ You will be able to do more with less saving the most valuable asset &ldquo;Time&rdquo;. By<br />learning effective research techniques collecting as many relevant information<br />to your topic, how to analyze and organize your ideas to structure your speech<br />effectively matching your audience.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Dates : 13,20 &amp; 27 May 2022</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(128, 'Payroll Preparation & Analysis', 2500, '2022-05-14', '2022-05-28', '10:00:00', '15:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645190904.png', 19, 0, '2022-02-21 04:20:28', '2022-02-18 13:28:24', '<p>&bull; Employee costs from payroll and other benefits are among the largest costs<br />in any company other than the Cost of Goods Sold (COGS), rent and<br />depreciation. This workshop starts with introductions about the departments<br />of HR and \'accounting and finance\' then focuses on the payroll function.<br />&bull; The workshop goes through the process of preparing and calculating payroll<br />and includes the controls needed and the pre-checks necessary to make sure<br />correct data is used.<br />&bull; The workshop explains how to conduct analysis on payroll and benefits using<br />Excel.<br />&bull; The course ends with ways to prepare budgets for the department and payroll<br />and benefit costs of the corporation.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Explain how the HR and accounting and finance functions contribute<br />to their success<br />&bull; Prepare the monthly payroll and review it for accuracy<br />&bull; Calculate taxes, social insurances, employee benefits, loans<br />vacations and End of Service Benefits (EOSB)<br />&bull; Reconcile payroll with accounting and audit the supporting<br />documents for payments<br />&bull; Develop monthly and annual payroll budgets<br />&bull; Design periodic payroll management reports and analysis</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 14,21 &amp; 28 May 2022</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
