(134, 'Selling Skills', 2800, '2022-05-23', '2022-05-24', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645974347.png', 16, 0, '2022-02-27 15:05:47', '2022-02-19 19:28:03', '<p>This Workshop provides participants with core knowledge about sales as a<br />function and as a process; this means that participants will get solid exposure<br />to sales and its contribution to company growth. In addition, participants will<br />acquire several skills related to negotiating deals, overcoming obstacles,<br />resolving customer issues and closing sales.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Identify and adopt the right professional selling behaviors and skills needed<br />to maximize sales performance<br />&bull; Develop critical self-driven practices to optimize personal and business<br />effectiveness and efficiency<br />&bull; Master and implement the sales process to successfully handle objections<br />and close more deals<br />&bull; Manage customer expectations and exceed it to gain customer loyalty and<br />generate repeat business<br />&bull; Master the art of verbal and non-verbal communication to create<br />atmosphere of respect and trust in the seller-buyer interface</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 23 &amp; 24 May 2022</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(135, 'Accountability & Ownership', 2500, '2022-05-25', '2022-05-26', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645974292.png', 9, 0, '2022-02-27 15:04:53', '2022-02-19 19:31:10', '<p>&bull; It&rsquo;s no wonder that organizations who promote accountability<br />are more successful and more productive. In this Employee<br />Accountability workshop.<br />&bull; You will learn about what accountability is how to promote it in<br />your organization, and how to become more accountable to<br />yourself and others.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :</p>\r\n<p>● Understand what accountability is and what events in history have<br />shaped our view of it<br />● Identify the requirements for personal and corporate accountability<br />● Apply the cycle of accountability and the fundamental elements required<br />to build an accountable organization<br />● Describe what individuals must do to become accountable<br />● Build skills required for accountability, including goal setting, giving and<br />receiving<br />● feedback, and delegation<br />● Pinpoint ways to build ownership in your organization<br />● Isolate areas for further self-improvement</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 25 &amp; 26 May 2022</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
