(152, 'Supervisory Skills', 2800, '2022-08-17', '2022-08-18', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1658929965.jpg', 12, 0, '2022-08-11 09:46:15', '2022-02-19 20:52:10', '<p>&bull; The workshop is designed to provide learners with highly effective tools &amp;<br />techniques that improve the essential supervisory skills your team needs,<br />both managerial &amp; people&rsquo;s skills - to strengthen teamwork, team<br />performance &amp; organizational success.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Identify the supervision functions<br />&bull; Create a planning network diagram<br />&bull; Describe the elements of planning<br />&bull; Apply the principles &amp;amp; approaches of organizing work<br />&bull; Use IDEALS Delegation Model to empower the team<br />&bull; Describe the control process, types &amp;amp; challenges<br />&bull; Apply tools to fix team performance<br />&bull; Demonstrate coaching skills &amp;amp; mentoring characteristics</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 17 &amp; 18 August 2022</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 1),
(153, 'Self Awareness & Self Confidence', 2500, '2022-08-17', '2022-08-18', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645972660.png', 9, 0, '2022-02-27 14:37:41', '2022-02-19 20:55:37', '<p>Healthy self-esteem and self-confidence are essential for growth and achieving<br />success. Of all the judgments you make in life, none is as important as the one<br />you make about yourself. Without some measure of self-worth, life can be painful<br />and unrelenting. This highly interactive workshop is designed to help the learners<br />discover some techniques that can help them feel better about themselves and<br />improve their self-esteem and self-confidence.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Describe the four archetypes of Self-awareness<br />&bull; Process emotions in healthy ways &amp; develop Emotional Agility<br />&bull; Develop techniques for eliminating unhealthy thought patterns and replacing<br />them with supportive patterns<br />&bull; Act more assertively and understand why this is important to self-esteem<br />&bull; and self-confidence&bull; Deal with setbacks in a way that does not damage self-esteem<br />&bull; Set goals that reflect your dreams and desires and reinforce healthy patterns</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 17 &amp; 18 August 2022</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(154, 'Setting Budget and Forecasting', 2500, '2022-08-14', '2022-08-16', '10:00:00', '14:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645691698.png', 17, 0, '2022-02-24 08:34:58', '2022-02-19 21:00:12', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 14,15,&amp; 16 August 2022</p>', 'Virtual', 'eg', 0),
(155, 'Purchasing & Cost Saving Techniques', 2500, '2022-08-16', '2022-08-19', '10:00:00', '14:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1660132105.png', 18, 0, '2022-08-10 11:48:25', '2022-02-19 21:14:24', '<p>Managing the purchasing department of the 21st Century is not an easy task. Today\'s global economy makes the purchasing function increasingly complicated. In this workshop, we will explore how to manage the various suppliers that may be located thousands of kilometers from your plant while achieving real cost savings. Furthermore, we will discover how the purchasing department fits in the overall function of the supply chain operation. Lastly, we will cover how the purchasing department should be managed properly to achieve all of its Key Performance Indicators (KPIs).</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Define the strategic role of the purchasing department</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Perform accurate supplier evaluation</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Develop effective negotiation strategies with all suppliers</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Explain the importance of value analysis to purchasing</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Evaluate the performance of the department using proper Key Performance Indicators (KPIs)</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Improve the efficiency of the purchasing department</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 16,17 &amp; 18 August 2022</p>', 'Virtual', 'eg', 0),
(156, 'Public Speaking : Express to impress (BY SPS', 4500, '2022-08-21', '2022-08-23', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645691568.png', 9, 0, '2022-02-24 08:32:48', '2022-02-19 21:17:00', '<p>◘ As young professional seeking excellence in your professional world, public<br />speaking is a vital skill to your success and your business as well. You won&rsquo;t be<br />concerned anymore about how to overcome challenges in presenting yourself<br />and your ideas in different situations.<br />◘ Whether it&rsquo;s a meeting with your managers and co-workers or communicating<br />with other departments and customers on behalf of your entity. And because<br />Such situations require a powerful set of skills to be able to express and<br />impress!<br />◘ In our program, we will help you gaining all these required skills which will<br />positively impact all other elements of your professional development journey<br />to establish yourself as a valuable member in your organization.<br />◘ You will gain more confidence in yourself by mastering your verbal and<br />nonverbal communication aspects, asking the right questions to understand<br />and validate the received information.<br />◘ You will be able to do more with less saving the most valuable asset &ldquo;Time&rdquo;. By<br />learning effective research techniques collecting as many relevant information<br />to your topic, how to analyze and organize your ideas to structure your speech<br />effectively matching your audience.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 21,22 &amp; 23 August 2022</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(157, 'Sales planning & Forecasting', 2500, '2022-08-21', '2022-08-23', '10:00:00', '14:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645691401.png', 16, 0, '2022-02-24 08:30:01', '2022-02-19 21:19:40', '<p>&bull; This is a sales planning and forecasting workshop that<br />covers both qualitative and basic quantitative aspects such<br />as the planning process and forecasting techniques. This<br />workshop aims to help the sales professionals better<br />understand the planning process and use better forecasting<br />techniques for existing as well as new products.<br />&bull; It focuses on improving organization and forecasting skills,<br />as well as other technical competencies aimed at guiding<br />salespeople towards higher performance.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Demonstrate traits of an excellent sales manager facing modern<br />market challenges<br />&bull; Design and deliver sales strategies, organize sales territories,<br />and use different forecasting models to optimize sales results<br />&bull; Know Planning function and process best practices<br />&bull; Know Techniques of organizing Sales Force</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 21,22 &amp; 23 August 2022</p>', 'Virtual', 'eg', 0),
(158, 'Handling Customer Complains', 2200, '2022-08-22', '2022-08-25', '12:00:00', '15:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645691354.png', 15, 0, '2022-02-24 08:29:14', '2022-02-19 21:22:26', '<p>&bull; Handling difficult customers can be a challenging task especially if it is<br />charged with irrational emotion. Often, the natural reaction would be to feel<br />defensive and try explaining why the situation occurred. More often than not,<br />this kind of reaction only make the situation go worse. This workshop is<br />designed to help the participants get into of their customers, understand their<br />pain and expectation, understand their preferences &amp; priorities, in order to<br />deliver a service that exceeds their expectations and fulfill both their<br />materialistic &amp; emotional needs.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :</p>\r\n<p>&bull;Define customer service and how to use this understanding to CS in handling<br />customers<br />&bull;Use the RATER Framework to enhance the Customers experience<br />&bull;Develop a Customer Journey Map<br />&bull;Describe the essential skillset for CS<br />&bull;Identify the four types of customers and how to handle each effectively</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 22,23,24 &amp; 25 August 2022</p>', 'Virtual', 'eg', 0);
