(176, 'Setting KPI`s & Managing Performance', 2800, '2022-07-25', '2022-07-26', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1657026883.png', 19, 0, '2022-07-05 13:14:44', '2022-02-20 20:55:19', '<p>&bull; This workshop addresses the three cornerstones of<br />excellent performance namely, the right set of Key<br />Performance Indicators (KPIs), the proper means of<br />tracking progress and the most effective methodologies<br />for intervention and feedback.</p>\r\n<p>&bull; By learning how to skillfully handle each of these tasks,<br />team leaders, supervisors or managers will be able to<br />directly and positively influence performance in their<br />units, sections, or departments.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; List the main criteria for measuring performance and use them to plan<br />and manage the performance of others<br />&bull; Design reporting mechanisms which are critical for measuring progress<br />and use them to track performance and determine critical deviations<br />&bull; Provide effective feedback as a means of dealing with individual<br />performance gaps and as a tool for effectively addressing all unfavorable<br />changes in performance<br />&bull; Determine when to coach and when to counsel and then do so based on<br />a thorough understanding of performance gaps and their root causes</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 25 &amp; 26 July 2022</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
