(179, 'Compensation & Benefits', 5000, '2022-07-03', '2022-07-07', '12:00:00', '15:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645391249.PNG', 19, 0, '2022-02-20 21:07:29', '2022-02-20 21:07:29', '<p>&bull; In this workshop, you will learn about the only part of human resources that<br />works behind the scenes.<br />Compensation and benefits is usually a function that professionals in the field<br />typically avoid for its seemingly complex nature and dependency on<br />mathematics.</p>\r\n<p>&bull; When you attend this Workshop, you will change your mind about this HR<br />specialty. We will explain the specifics of compensation and benefits in such a<br />way that you be able to apply them easily at work.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Explain the basic principles and major elements of<br />compensation<br />&bull;Apply the various processes in compensation: job analysis, job<br />descriptions and job evaluation<br />&bull;Explain what constitutes a sound and effective compensation<br />and benefits program<br />&bull;Describe the basic compensation survey process</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 03, 04,05 , 06 &amp; 07 July 2022</p>', 'Virtual', 'eg', 0),
(180, 'Payroll Preparation & Analysis', 2500, '2022-09-03', '2022-09-17', '10:00:00', '15:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645608390.png', 19, 0, '2022-02-23 09:26:31', '2022-02-20 21:12:19', '<p>&bull; Employee costs from payroll and other benefits are among the largest costs<br />in any company other than the Cost of Goods Sold (COGS), rent and<br />depreciation. This workshop starts with introductions about the departments<br />of HR and \'accounting and finance\' then focuses on the payroll function.<br />&bull; The workshop goes through the process of preparing and calculating payroll<br />and includes the controls needed and the pre-checks necessary to make sure<br />correct data is used.<br />&bull; The workshop explains how to conduct analysis on payroll and benefits using<br />Excel.<br />&bull; The course ends with ways to prepare budgets for the department and payroll<br />and benefit costs of the corporation.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Explain how the HR and accounting and finance functions contribute<br />to their success<br />&bull; Prepare the monthly payroll and review it for accuracy<br />&bull; Calculate taxes, social insurances, employee benefits, loans<br />vacations and End of Service Benefits (EOSB)<br />&bull; Reconcile payroll with accounting and audit the supporting<br />documents for payments<br />&bull; Develop monthly and annual payroll budgets<br />&bull; Design periodic payroll management reports and analysis</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 03,10 &amp; 17 Sep 2022</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(181, 'Business Agility', 2500, '2022-09-04', '2022-09-06', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645608298.png', 11, 0, '2022-02-25 18:56:29', '2022-02-20 21:15:25', '<p>The shortest and briefest definition of Agility is the inherent ability to respond to<br />change. But does that mean in Business World?<br />Can you think of a company that has gone bust? Nokia, Kodak? You&rsquo;ve probably heard<br />of more examples, there are loads of them out there! Big names like these have failed<br />to cope with the rapid changes and therefore were doomed to fail.<br />Now, more than ever before, organizations need to reinvent themselves to cope with<br />the ever-changing nature of the workplace.<br />This highly interactive workshop is designed to raise the participants&rsquo; awareness of<br />Business Agility &amp; it&rsquo;s best practices. The learning process is based on real-world<br />business cases like McDonalds, Panadol, Mazda, Apple, Harley Davidson &amp; more.<br />Participants will also acquire the knowledge &amp; tools needed to create an action plan to<br />meet ambiguity with agility in order implement new approaches such as Business<br />Model Canvas &amp; Blue Ocean Strategy that transforms an undesired situation into an<br />opportunity.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Recognize the importance of leading agile and resilient organizations during<br />turbulent times<br />&bull; Make decisions in chaotic situations<br />&bull; Use problem solving tools to provide effective solutions<br />&bull; Identify ambiguity in business and adapt it to agility<br />&bull; Lead and develop proactive mechanisms to withstand environmental<br />disruptions<br />&bull; Create compelling strategies to lead and drive agility and resilience<br />&bull; Use Business Model Canvas &amp; Blue Ocean Strategy to create value<br />&bull; Demonstrate agile leadership skills in the modern world</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 04 , 05 &amp; 06 Sep 2022</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(182, 'Email Writing Techniques', 2500, '2022-09-04', '2022-09-07', '12:00:00', '15:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1661353536.jpeg', 13, 0, '2022-08-24 15:05:36', '2022-02-20 21:18:46', '<p>In business writing, the language is concrete, the point of view is clear, and the<br />points are well expressed. This workshop is designed to provide the learners<br />with a proven step-by-step process, to write faster and more effectively.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Apply the basic tools of writing for effective outcome<br />&bull; Develop a technical writing style<br />&bull; Identify the different types of writing<br />&bull; Avoid common mistakes in technical writing<br />&bull; Demonstrate an understanding of formal language required for business<br />Communication</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 04,05,06 &amp; 07 Sep 2022</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
