(184, 'Business Etiquette - Doing  Business with Class', 2500, '2022-09-07', '2022-09-08', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645392574.PNG', 9, 0, '2022-02-21 04:11:31', '2022-02-20 21:29:34', '<p>Have you ever had to make small talk with a Very Important Person and been<br />lost for words?<br />If the answer is yes, then you know just how agonizing some moments can be.<br />Even worse (and what can be even more damaging to your career) are the<br />social gaffes you aren&rsquo;t even aware you make.<br />This highly interactive workshop will help you handle most of those socially<br />difficult moments. You&rsquo;ll have an extra edge in areas you may not have given a<br />lot of thought to before.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Differentiate between ethics, manners and etiquette<br />&bull; Identify the significance of etiquette and manners in business<br />&bull; Develop right professional image<br />&bull; Identify how to manage the workstation<br />&bull; Describe how to behave in Open Area office set-up<br />&bull; Apply proper communication etiquette<br />&bull; Display proper techniques towards universal behavior etiquette<br />&bull; Demonstrate appropriate personal and professional conduct<br />&bull; Identify how to represent the Corporate Branding</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 07 &amp; 08 Sep 2022</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(185, 'Public Speaking : Express to Impress (BY SPS)', 4200, '2022-09-11', '2022-09-20', '18:00:00', '21:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645604844.png', 9, 0, '2022-02-23 08:27:25', '2022-02-20 21:35:01', '<p>◘ As young professional seeking excellence in your professional world, public<br />speaking is a vital skill to your success and your business as well. You won&rsquo;t be<br />concerned anymore about how to overcome challenges in presenting yourself<br />and your ideas in different situations.<br />◘ Whether it&rsquo;s a meeting with your managers and co-workers or communicating<br />with other departments and customers on behalf of your entity. And because<br />Such situations require a powerful set of skills to be able to express and<br />impress!<br />◘ In our program, we will help you gaining all these required skills which will<br />positively impact all other elements of your professional development journey<br />to establish yourself as a valuable member in your organization.<br />◘ You will gain more confidence in yourself by mastering your verbal and<br />nonverbal communication aspects, asking the right questions to understand<br />and validate the received information.<br />◘ You will be able to do more with less saving the most valuable asset &ldquo;Time&rdquo;. By<br />learning effective research techniques collecting as many relevant information<br />to your topic, how to analyze and organize your ideas to structure your speech<br />effectively matching your audience.</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 11,13,15,18,20 &amp; 22 Sep 2022</p>', 'Virtual', 'eg', 0),
(186, 'Strategic Accountant Management', 2800, '2022-09-11', '2022-09-12', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645604624.png', 16, 0, '2022-02-23 08:23:44', '2022-02-20 21:39:06', '<p>This highly interactive workshop is designed to raise the participants&rsquo;<br />awareness of Key Account Management &amp; it&rsquo;s best practices. Participants will<br />acquire the knowledge &amp; tools needed to Identify accounts with the greatest<br />potential for growth, developing strategies to grow them, building essential<br />customer relationships, and bring value to customers. At the same time,<br />growing sales by selling more to existing accounts.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Identify the main functions of key accounts and how they are aligned to the<br />business organization<br />&bull; Define and prioritize key accounts to measure their profitability and strategic<br />importance to a company<br />&bull; Classify customer relations levels to improve the way Account Managers<br />deal with customers<br />&bull; Establish customer focused plans and strategies needed to develop key<br />accounts<br />&bull; Determine the functional role of key account managers in facing the<br />changing challenges in the market</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 11&amp; 12 Sep 2022</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(187, 'Your 720 Min Guide for Time Management', 2500, '2022-09-13', '2022-09-14', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645604546.png', 9, 0, '2022-02-23 08:22:27', '2022-02-21 20:06:15', '<p>This interactive workshop is designed to help the<br />participants explore various time management skills and<br />stress management techniques to get better control and<br />have a more positive impact over their time at the<br />professional and social levels.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Identify time management challenges and assess their efficiency in managing their time<br />&bull; Use Time Management Matrix for better time management<br />&bull; Analyze stress symptoms and their causes in order to identify their negative impact<br />&bull; Recognize Delegation rules &amp; tools<br />&bull; Apply time-saving techniques to stop wasting time<br />&bull; Apply STOP practice in stressful situations</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Dates : 13 &amp; 14 Sep 2022&nbsp;</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0);
