(188, 'Excel Master - Advanced Level', 1800, '2022-09-15', '2022-09-29', '10:00:00', '15:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645604425.jpg', 14, 0, '2022-02-23 08:20:26', '2022-02-21 20:08:47', '<p>&bull; This Workshop is designed to focus on the advanced<br />Excel tools And features that goes beyond the basics<br />and enable users to go from only editing and formatting<br />sheets to creating their own Advanced calculations and<br />reports instead of working one Previously prepared<br />ones<br />&bull; Also you will check in this workshop the different<br />powerful tools that make you the Master of Excel</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Mastering Excel most important functions<br />&bull; Analyzing Data and Alternative data sets<br />&bull; Apply the key Excel functions to prepare data for analysis<br />&bull; Apply advanced calculations<br />&bull; Create and customize pivot tables to reconcile and analyze<br />accounts efficiently<br />&bull; Utilize pivot tables functions and calculations to generate a<br />set of management and business analysis reports<br />&bull; Creating Advanced charts and graphics<br />&bull; Changing workbook Appearance</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 15, 22 &amp; 29 Sep 2022</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(189, 'Advanced  Sales Professional', 3200, '2022-09-18', '2022-09-29', '12:00:00', '15:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645604349.png', 16, 0, '2022-02-23 08:19:10', '2022-02-21 20:11:34', '<p>&bull; This Workshop provides participants with core knowledge about sales as a<br />function and as a process; this means that participants will get solid exposure<br />to sales and its contribution to company growth.<br />&bull; In addition, participants will acquire several skills related to negotiating deals,<br />overcoming obstacles, resolving customer issues and closing sales.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>● Identify and adopt the right professional selling behaviors and skills<br />needed to maximize sales performance<br />● Develop critical self-driven practices to optimize personal and<br />business effectiveness and efficiency<br />● Master and implement the sales process to successfully handle<br />objections and close more deals<br />● Manage customer expectations and exceed it to gain customer<br />loyalty and generate repeat business<br />● Master the art of verbal and non-verbal communication to create<br />an atmosphere of respect and trust in the seller-buyer interface</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 18,20,22,25 , 27 &amp; 29 Sep 2022&nbsp;</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(190, 'Design Thinking - Unlock Innovation', 3500, '2022-09-19', '2022-09-20', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645604280.png', 9, 0, '2022-02-23 08:18:01', '2022-02-21 20:15:00', '<p>Design thinking is a powerful process of problem solving, a journey that begins<br />with having an empathic understanding of unmet customer needs. From that<br />insight emerges a blend of Heart, Head and Hand process that is based on<br />vision,<br />continuing on to development, applied creativity, prototyping then diving into<br />experimentation, practical creation &amp;amp; testing. This highly interactive<br />workshop is<br />designed to help the participants learn a proven, systematic approach to new<br />product development through a process that puts unmet customer needs at the<br />center of the problem. It also helps them apply design thinking approaches to<br />business, so that the success rate for innovation can improve substantially.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Use Design Thinking to solve problems more creatively<br />&bull; Understand problems from the customers perspective<br />&bull; Apply different brainstorming techniques to identify innovative ideas<br />&bull; Use effective design research<br />&bull; Understand the value of creating prototypes to test your ideas<br />&bull; Keep your design ideas moving forward</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 19 &amp; 20 Sep 2022&nbsp;</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(191, 'Successful Thinking & Planning', 2800, '2022-09-20', '2022-09-22', '10:00:00', '14:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645474733.PNG', 10, 0, '2022-02-21 20:18:53', '2022-02-21 20:18:53', '<p>&bull; In this workshop, we will cover the steps of the strategy management<br />process, starting with the \'thinking\' components of strategy, moving into the<br />\'planning\' components and ending with \'execution\',<br />&bull; Participants will be able to implement or improve the strategic process at their<br />organizations to reach their vision and achieve their mission.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :</p>\r\n<p>● Apply strategic thinking to analyze their current environment and<br />determine their organizational ambition<br />● Employ the strategic management process to best achieve the desired<br />ambition<br />● Assess and choose strategies that create a sustainable competitive<br />advantage for the organization<br />● Determine strategic objectives, Key Performance Indicators (KPIs)<br />and \'SMART\' targets for the organization<br />● Convert strategic plans to operating plans through creating strategic<br />initiatives and sequencing activities</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 20,21 &amp; 22 Sep 2022</p>', 'Virtual', 'eg', 0),
(192, 'Recruitment Best Practice', 3500, '2022-09-23', '2022-09-24', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1661671786.png', 19, 0, '2022-08-28 07:29:47', '2022-02-21 20:21:25', '<p>&bull; The function of recruitment and selection plays a key<br />role in the entry of new employees into the organization.<br />As such, it has an overwhelming influence on the<br />successful achievement of organizational objectives.<br />This workshop will show you the logical and correct<br />steps you must take to structure and implement<br />recruitment best practices.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Define recruitment and selection and the important role this<br />function plays in the success of an organization<br />&bull; List the main steps that should be followed to develop an<br />effective recruitment plan and select the best methods and<br />sources for attracting qualified candidates<br />&bull; Choose the most appropriate techniques for short listing<br />and assessing candidates considering the reliability and<br />validity of each<br />&bull; Implement the right measures and Key Performance<br />Indicators (KPIs) to evaluate the effectiveness of<br />recruitment efforts<br />&bull; Discuss how to be an Employer of Choice</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 23 &amp; 24 &nbsp;Sep 2022</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(193, 'Accountability & Ownership', 2200, '2022-09-25', '2022-09-27', '10:00:00', '14:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645475104.PNG', 9, 0, '2022-02-21 20:25:05', '2022-02-21 20:25:05', '<p>&bull; It&rsquo;s no wonder that organizations who promote accountability<br />are more successful and more productive. In this Employee<br />Accountability workshop.<br />&bull; You will learn about what accountability is how to promote it in<br />your organization, and how to become more accountable to<br />yourself and others.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>● Understand what accountability is and what events in history have<br />shaped our view of it<br />● Identify the requirements for personal and corporate accountability<br />● Apply the cycle of accountability and the fundamental elements required<br />to build an accountable organization<br />● Describe what individuals must do to become accountable<br />● Build skills required for accountability, including goal setting, giving and<br />receiving<br />● feedback, and delegation<br />● Pinpoint ways to build ownership in your organization<br />● Isolate areas for further self-improvement</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 25 , 26 &amp; 27 Sep 2022&nbsp;</p>', 'Virtual', 'eg', 0),
(194, 'Finance for Non Financials', 2800, '2022-09-25', '2022-09-26', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645603893.png', 17, 0, '2022-02-23 08:11:33', '2022-02-21 20:29:10', '<p>&bull; This Workshop transforms financial and accounting concepts into<br />decision making tools you can unsuccessfully every day. You will<br />learn to apply the fundamentals of finance to improve budget<br />management, increase potential profits, and assess the financial<br />performance of business activities. You will also understand the<br />terminology used by accounting and finance staff and will feel<br />more confident when being involved with them or using them<br />&bull; Professionals/Managers with a financial background are considered<br />most efficient at managing any operating scenario. Knowledge of<br />financial aspects that help in decision making is the key to their<br />success. It is important for a senior professional to be equipped with<br />financial decision-making tools to be able to analyze financial<br />statements, understand the nature of cost and ways to reduce cost,<br />take pricing decisions, decide a product mix and opt for the best<br />suited option of financing the need.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Define the four key financial statements: balance sheet,<br />income statement, cash flow and changes in owner equity<br />&bull; Interpret the financial health and condition of a<br />company, division or responsibility center and use<br />financial information for management and evaluation<br />&bull; Distinguish between accounting and finance and<br />explain the finance role in running businesses<br />&bull; Prepare a company\'s operating budget and relate it to<br />the organization\'s strategic objectives<br />&bull; Apply Financial techniques to enhance decision making</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(