(195, 'Logistics  Operations', 2500, '2022-09-28', '2022-09-29', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645475511.PNG', 18, 0, '2022-02-21 20:31:51', '2022-02-21 20:31:51', '<p>&bull; Logistics Operations is an essential function governing the flow of goods<br />through a supply chain.<br />&bull; This workshop brings you up to date with the latest logistics models and<br />practices. The workshop&rsquo;s main focus is on the optimization of transport,<br />warehouse and inventory management activities</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Recognize modern supply chain and logistics trends as a basis for<br />sustainable performance<br />&bull; Employ qualitative and quantitative material forecasting techniques for a<br />streamlined logistical operation<br />&bull; Describe role of transportation in logistics and identify opportunities for<br />operational improvement<br />&bull; Identify the role of warehousing, focusing on operational throughput and<br />performance optimization<br />&bull; Recognize role of import and Export in logistics<br />&bull; Describe information needed in custom Procedures and Documentations<br />&bull; Apply performance measurements to manage strategic, operational and<br />tactical facets of logistics</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Dates : 28 &amp; 29 Sep 2022&nbsp;</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
