(199, 'Project Management', 5800, '2022-10-02', '2022-10-18', '10:00:00', '14:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645601720.png', 10, 0, '2022-02-23 07:35:21', '2022-02-21 20:53:19', '<p>&bull; The overall aim of this workshop is to provide participants with the necessary<br />skills required to plan their projects by creating project scope statements and<br />project work breakdown structures. Additionally, participants will learn how to<br />develop key performance indicators for monitoring and controlling their project<br />schedule and budget.<br />&bull; The workshop also aims at assisting participants in appraising the feasibility<br />of their projects by applying capital budgeting techniques. Finally, the<br />workshop will cover how to effectively plan project stakeholders&rsquo; engagement<br />and manage their expectations.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p> Plan projects using statement of work and Work Breakdown Structure<br />(WBS)<br /> Schedule projects activities and build the project network model<br /> Calculate project budgets and schedule variances using Earned Value<br />(EV) Techniques<br /> Select the right projects using capital budgeting techniques<br /> Relate to project stakeholders through better negotiation and<br />communication skills</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 02,04,09,11,16 &amp; 18 October 2022&nbsp;</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
