(217, 'Super Trainer', 7200, '2022-11-06', '2022-11-27', '18:00:00', '21:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645599889.png', 9, 0, '2022-02-23 07:04:50', '2022-02-21 22:04:46', '<p>Designed in a highly interactive style, this workshop provides the<br />trainers with the knowledge and skills they need to plan and execute<br />training sessions. The journey of a trainer on this workshop starts with<br />an understanding of how adults learn and progresses through different<br />learning styles, trainer skills, learning strategies, tasks and exercises,<br />and the debriefing process.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; List various adult learning principles and their implications on the delivery<br />of training<br />&bull; Identify and develop skills required in successful trainers<br />&bull; Examine training methods and determine the most appropriate for their<br />training workshops<br />&bull; Write specific instructional learning objectives (ILOs)<br />&bull; Apply training models in the design and delivery of training courses<br />&bull; Develop blueprints for training sessions<br />&bull; Plan and deliver a training session relevant to their areas of expertise</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 06,08,10,13,15,17,20,22,24 &amp; 27 Nov 2022</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(218, 'Writing Reports & Proposals', 2800, '2022-11-06', '2022-11-07', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645599825.png', 13, 0, '2022-02-23 07:03:46', '2022-02-21 22:07:22', '<p>It is essential to understand how to write reports and proposals that get read. We<br />write reports in a range of formats and a variety of purposes. Whether you need<br />to report on a product analysis, inventory, feasibility studies, or something else,<br />report writing is a skill you will use again and again.<br />Having a method to prepare these documents will help you be as efficient as<br />possible with the task. This highly interactive workshop will build on a solid base<br />of writing skills to present information in formal, informal, and proposal styles.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Prepare Reports And Proposals That Inform, Persuade, and Provide<br />Information.<br />&bull; Review Your Work So That It Is Clear, Concise, Complete, and Correct.<br />&bull; Apply Business Writing Skills in Real Work Applications<br />&bull; Employ The Best Approach For Winning a Proposal<br />&bull; Describe &amp; Follow The Four Stages of Writing A Report<br />&bull; Create a Winning Design that Gets Responses</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 06 &amp; 07 Nov 2022</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(219, 'Selling Skills', 2800, '2022-11-08', '2022-11-09', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645599739.png', 16, 0, '2022-02-23 07:02:19', '2022-02-21 22:13:10', '<p>&bull; This Workshop provides participants with core knowledge about sales as a<br />function and as a process; this means that participants will get solid exposure<br />to sales and its contribution to company growth. In addition, participants will<br />acquire several skills related to negotiating deals, overcoming obstacles,<br />resolving customer issues and closing sales.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Identify and adopt the right professional selling behaviors and skills needed<br />to maximize sales performance<br />&bull; Develop critical self-driven practices to optimize personal and business<br />effectiveness and efficiency<br />&bull; Master and implement the sales process to successfully handle objections<br />and close more deals<br />&bull; Manage customer expectations and exceed it to gain customer loyalty and<br />generate repeat business<br />&bull; Master the art of verbal and non-verbal communication to create<br />atmosphere of respect and trust in the seller-buyer interface</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 08 &amp; 09 Nov 2022</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(220, 'Crucial Conversation', 3200, '2022-11-13', '2022-11-16', '12:00:00', '15:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645599368.png', 9, 0, '2022-02-23 06:56:08', '2022-02-21 22:15:59', '<p>&bull; Many &lsquo;defining&rsquo; moments in life come from having crucial conversations,<br />which we anticipate will be difficult and which we may feel ill-equipped to<br />handle. We may also occasionally be involved in amicable conversations that<br />suddenly turn sour. Having the knowledge and confidence to deal with these<br />situations can make all the difference between a relationship fortified and a<br />relationship lost, or a sale made, and a sale lost.<br />&bull; This interactive workshop focuses on techniques on how to hold such<br />conversations in a positive space when surrounded by highly charged<br />emotions. It is designed to equip you with both the skillset and the confidence<br />you need to successfully manage crucial conversations and ensure that both<br />sides have the best chance of leaving the encounter feeling happy.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p> Define &amp; detect a Crucial Conversation<br /> Assess your usual approach to stress<br /> Recognize the power of Dialogue<br /> Recognize personal dialogue patterns &amp; change it into positive stories<br /> Use S.T.A.T.E &amp; AAMP techniques to tell your story &amp; learn the path of<br />others<br /> Handle disagreements effectively using the ABC Method<br /> Describe and practice methods to move from conversation to actions and<br />results</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 13,14,15 &amp; 16 Nov 2022</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
