(222, 'Payroll Preparation & Analysis', 2200, '2022-11-14', '2022-11-28', '18:00:00', '21:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645541700.png', 19, 0, '2022-02-22 14:55:01', '2022-02-21 22:22:06', '<p>&bull; Employee costs from payroll and other benefits are among the largest costs<br />in any company other than the Cost of Goods Sold (COGS), rent and<br />depreciation. This workshop starts with introductions about the departments<br />of HR and \'accounting and finance\' then focuses on the payroll function.<br />&bull; The workshop goes through the process of preparing and calculating payroll<br />and includes the controls needed and the pre-checks necessary to make sure<br />correct data is used.<br />&bull; The workshop explains how to conduct analysis on payroll and benefits using<br />Excel.<br />&bull; The course ends with ways to prepare budgets for the department and payroll<br />and benefit costs of the corporation.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Explain how the HR and accounting and finance functions contribute<br />to their success<br />&bull; Prepare the monthly payroll and review it for accuracy<br />&bull; Calculate taxes, social insurances, employee benefits, loans<br />vacations and End of Service Benefits (EOSB)<br />&bull; Reconcile payroll with accounting and audit the supporting<br />documents for payments<br />&bull; Develop monthly and annual payroll budgets<br />&bull; Design periodic payroll management reports and analysis</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 14,16,21,23 &amp; 28 Nov 2022</p>', 'Virtual', 'eg', 0),
