(235, 'Principles of Successful Negotiations', 2800, '2022-07-12', '2022-08-12', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645534594.png', 9, 0, '2022-02-22 12:56:35', '2022-02-22 06:24:58', '<p>&bull; Knowing how to negotiate effectively, and with confidence, is a skill that will<br />change everything. This highly interactive workshop is designed to provide<br />participants with the essential knowledge &amp; tools they need to know about<br />negotiation, step by methodical step. They&rsquo;ll also be armed with a set of<br />practical tools that you can start using right away to get better results in their<br />work and life in general.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Define Negotiation &amp; highlight its importance<br />&bull; Identify different negotiation models &amp; styles &amp; when to use each<br />&bull; Using a set of effective skills for better negotiation outcomes<br />&bull; Discover the appropriate negotiation style for each situation<br />&bull; Identify personal negotiation style &amp; other&rsquo;s</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 07 &amp; 08 Dec 2022&nbsp;</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(236, 'Supervisory Skills', 2500, '2022-12-11', '2022-12-13', '10:00:00', '14:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645534374.png', 12, 0, '2022-02-22 12:52:55', '2022-02-22 06:29:07', '<p>&bull; The workshop is designed to provide learners with highly effective tools &amp;<br />techniques that improve the essential supervisory skills your team needs,<br />both managerial &amp; people&rsquo;s skills - to strengthen teamwork, team<br />performance &amp; organizational success.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Identify the supervision functions<br />&bull; Create a planning network diagram<br />&bull; Describe the elements of planning<br />&bull; Apply the principles &amp;amp; approaches of organizing work<br />&bull; Use IDEALS Delegation Model to empower the team<br />&bull; Describe the control process, types &amp;amp; challenges<br />&bull; Apply tools to fix team performance<br />&bull; Demonstrate coaching skills &amp;amp; mentoring characteristics</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 11,12 &amp; 13 Dec 2022&nbsp;</p>', 'Virtual', 'eg', 0),
(237, 'Finance for Non Financials', 2500, '2022-12-11', '2022-12-14', '12:00:00', '15:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645534295.png', 17, 0, '2022-02-22 12:51:35', '2022-02-22 06:33:59', '<p>&bull; This Workshop transforms financial and accounting concepts into<br />decision making tools you can unsuccessfully every day. You will<br />learn to apply the fundamentals of finance to improve budget<br />management, increase potential profits, and assess the financial<br />performance of business activities. You will also understand the<br />terminology used by accounting and finance staff and will feel<br />more confident when being involved with them or using them<br />&bull; Professionals/Managers with a financial background are considered<br />most efficient at managing any operating scenario. Knowledge of<br />financial aspects that help in decision making is the key to their<br />success. It is important for a senior professional to be equipped with<br />financial decision-making tools to be able to analyze financial<br />statements, understand the nature of cost and ways to reduce cost,<br />take pricing decisions, decide a product mix and opt for the best<br />suited option of financing the need.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Define the four key financial statements: balance sheet,<br />income statement, cash flow and changes in owner equity<br />&bull; Interpret the financial health and condition of a<br />company, division or responsibility center and use<br />financial information for management and evaluation<br />&bull; Distinguish between accounting and finance and<br />explain the finance role in running businesses<br />&bull; Prepare a company\'s operating budget and relate it to<br />the organization\'s strategic objectives<br />&bull; Apply Financial techniques to enhance decision making</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 11,12,13 &amp; 14 Dec 2022</p>', 'Virtual', 'eg', 0),
(238, 'Customer Service Professional', 2500, '2022-12-18', '2022-12-27', '18:00:00', '21:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645534240.png', 15, 0, '2022-02-22 12:50:40', '2022-02-22 06:37:32', '<p>While many organizations promise to deliver an incredible customer experience,<br />some are better at supplying this than others. This two-day interactive workshop<br />is designed around six critical elements of customer service that, when a<br />company truly embraces them, bring customers back to experience service that<br />outdoes the competition.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Define customer service and its approach<br />&bull; Understand how your own behavior affects the behavior of others<br />&bull; Demonstrate confidence and skill as a problem solver<br />&bull; Apply techniques to deal with difficult customers<br />&bull; Know how to provide excellent customer service</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 18,20,25 &amp; 27 &nbsp;Dec 2022&nbsp;</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(239, 'Purchasing & Cost Saving Techniques', 2800, '2022-12-18', '2022-12-19', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645534171.png', 18, 0, '2022-02-22 12:49:32', '2022-02-22 06:39:45', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 18 &amp; 19 Dec 2022&nbsp;</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(240, 'Analytical Thinking', 2200, '2022-12-18', '2022-12-21', '12:00:00', '15:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645534092.png', 9, 0, '2022-02-22 12:48:13', '2022-02-22 06:53:31', '<p>In today&rsquo;s society, many people experience information overload. We are<br />bombarded with messages to believe various ideas, purchase things, support<br />causes, and lead our lifestyle in a particular way. How do you know what to<br />believe? How do you separate the truth from the myths?<br />The answer lies in analytical &amp; critical thinking skills. The ability to clearly reason<br />through problems and to present arguments in a logical, compelling way has<br />become a key skill for survival in today&rsquo;s world. This highly interactive workshop<br />will give you some practical tools and hands-on experience with critical thinking<br />and problem solving.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Define core concepts of analytical thinking</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Describe other thinking styles, including left/right brain thinking and whole-<br />brain thinking</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Work through the analytical thinking process to build or analyze arguments<br />&bull; Develop and evaluate explanations<br />&bull; Improve key analytical thinking skills, including active listening and<br />questioning<br />&bull; Prepare and present powerful arguments</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 18,19,20 &amp; 21 Dec 2022&nbsp;</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(241, 'The Pro Recruiter', 3500, '2022-12-19', '2022-12-28', '18:00:00', '21:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645512971.PNG', 19, 0, '2022-02-22 06:56:11', '2022-02-22 06:56:11', '<p>Build your strategic aspects of this important HR function. In this workshop It will show<br />you the logical and correct steps you must take to structure and implement<br />recruitment and selection practices and how to be a professional recruiter.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Define recruitment and selection and the important role this function plays in the<br />success of an organization<br />&bull; List the main steps that should be followed to develop an effective recruitment plan<br />and select the best methods and sources for attracting qualified candidates<br />&bull; Choose the most appropriate techniques for short listing and assessing candidates<br />considering the reliability and validity of each<br />&bull; Implement the right measures and Key Performance Indicators (KPIs) to evaluate<br />the effectiveness of recruitment efforts</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 19,21,26 &amp; 28 Dec 2022</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(242, 'Public Speaking : Express to Impress (BY SPS)', 4500, '2022-12-20', '2022-12-22', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645533351.png', 9, 0, '2022-02-22 12:35:51', '2022-02-22 06:59:35', '<p>◘ As young professional seeking excellence in your professional world, public<br />speaking is a vital skill to your success and your business as well. You won&rsquo;t be<br />concerned anymore about how to overcome challenges in presenting yourself<br />and your ideas in different situations.<br />◘ Whether it&rsquo;s a meeting with your managers and co-workers or communicating<br />with other departments and customers on behalf of your entity. And because<br />Such situations require a powerful set of skills to be able to express and<br />impress!<br />◘ In our program, we will help you gaining all these required skills which will<br />positively impact all other elements of your professional development journey<br />to establish yourself as a valuable member in your organization.<br />◘ You will gain more confidence in yourself by mastering your verbal and<br />nonverbal communication aspects, asking the right questions to understand<br />and validate the received information.<br />◘ You will be able to do more with less saving the most valuable asset &ldquo;Time&rdquo;. By<br />learning effective research techniques collecting as many relevant information<br />to your topic, how to analyze and organize your ideas to structure your speech<br />effectively matching your audience.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Dates : 21,22 &amp; 23 Dec 2022</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
