(244, 'Financial Analysis & Reporting', 2500, '2022-12-25', '2022-12-26', '10:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645533005.png', 17, 0, '2022-02-22 12:30:05', '2022-02-22 07:12:29', '<p>&bull; This workshop takes you from the first step of<br />understanding the relationships between the different<br />elements of financial statements, through calculating<br />and analyzing the financial ratios to the last step of<br />presenting recommendations.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Apply the framework of financial statements analysis<br />&bull; Use ratio and financial analysis<br />&bull; Interpret company financials and industry position<br />&bull; Appraise the process of company evaluation and analysis<br />&bull; Analyze real-life financial statements from companies<br />traded on the world stock exchanges<br />&bull; Prepare financial analysis template models</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 25 &amp; 26 Dec 2022&nbsp;</p>', 'Classroom', 'eg', 0),
(245, 'The Alpha Leader', 4200, '2022-12-27', '2022-12-30', '10:00:00', '14:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645532845.jpg', 12, 0, '2022-02-22 12:27:25', '2022-02-22 07:19:33', '<p>&bull; This highly interactive workshop is designed to prepare an Alpha Leader<br />through providing hands-on tools that ensure full understanding and<br />comprehension of the role of a leader as a source of empowerment for the<br />team, hence enhancing the overall team performance &amp; organizational<br />success.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Identify Personality Styles &amp; how to win with different styles<br />&bull; Link Leadership Styles with Maturity Levels of employees<br />&bull; Develop key management competencies required for the execution of<br />basics tasks and activities<br />&bull; Set SMART Goals and evaluate performance against them<br />&bull; Use Time Management Matrix to set priorities<br />&bull; Apply coaching techniques to boost productivity and optimize outcomes<br />&bull; Demonstrate skills of Strategic Leaders</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you want full outlines contact us on the below numbers :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>T:</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:(202)%2025281172\">(202) 25281172</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>M:</strong>&nbsp;01012769079 - 01016445898 &ndash; 01009779374 &ndash; 01019330540</p>\r\n<p><strong>Email :</strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:training@skills\">training@skillsbankme.com</a></p>', '<p>Dates : 27,28,29 &amp; 30 Dec 2022&nbsp;</p>', 'Virtual', 'eg', 0),
(246, 'HR Policies & Procedures', 430, '2022-07-03', '2022-07-07', '14:00:00', '17:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645973656.png', 19, 0, '2022-05-11 11:34:02', '2022-02-22 17:54:11', '<p>&nbsp;Writing human resources policies and procedures is both an art and a science. &nbsp;&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;<br />This workshop will equip you with the knowledge and skills you need to complete this challenging task inhouse. If you still decide to outsource this activity, you will benefit from this course by learning how to ensure the policies and procedures produced by the third party are written in the right manner for your organization.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objcetives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; List all human resources functions and responsibilities and identify their<br />contributions to organizational success<br />&bull; Explain the difference between policies, processes and procedures<br />&bull; Apply appropriate HR policies and procedures writing techniques<br />&bull; Describe the purpose and usefulness of human resources policies and<br />procedures<br />&bull; Develop human resources policies and procedures</p>', '<p>Dates : 03, 04,05 , 06 &amp; 07 July 2022&nbsp;</p>', 'Classroom', 'sa', 0),
(247, 'The Power Of Positive Attitude', 400, '2022-07-12', '2022-07-14', '12:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1652268800.png', 9, 0, '2022-05-11 11:33:21', '2022-02-22 17:57:42', '<p>Positive thinking and attitudes can increase both your personal and business<br />results and achievements. New business requirements, increased performance<br />demands and a changing workforce mean it is essential for professionals at all<br />levels to understand and master the skills, techniques and methods of positive<br />thinking and positive attitude.<br />Recent studies in behavioral science and neuroscience reveal scientific proof<br />and evidence of the power of a positive mental attitude. Research also tells us<br />that high achievers have trained themselves in this vital attitude. This interactive<br />and highly practical workshop gives you a step-by-step method to cultivate the<br />power of a positive thinking and attitude. It will also provide you with many<br />practical insights and tools to manage and develop others as well.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Examine the impact of positive attitude on personal and professional<br />environments<br />&bull; List the steps needed for improving attitude and behavior<br />&bull; Apply positive psychology techniques to improve effectiveness on the job<br />&bull; Identify preferred thinking patterns and filters<br />&bull; Use techniques to improve relationships with others</p>', '<p>Dates : 12,13 &amp; 14 July 2022&nbsp;</p>', 'Virtual', 'sa', 0);
