(248, 'Data Analysis & Reporting Techniques Using Excel', 280, '2022-07-17', '2022-07-28', '15:00:00', '18:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1652259068.png', 14, 0, '2022-05-11 10:45:05', '2022-02-22 18:16:24', '<p>&bull; It is no surprise for corporate staff to be staff to be overwhelmed by the<br />abundance of instructed data.</p>\r\n<p>&bull; ERPs and database have evolved to a point where they can house<br />amazingly large amounts of data the question now is, what do you do<br />with this data to add value .</p>\r\n<p>&bull; this workshop will introduce business intelligence (BI), hands on, to<br />allow you to clean, normalize, interpret, analyze and report large volumes<br />of data. you will be able to establish historical relationships, analyze the<br />current situation and predict future strategies .</p>\r\n<p>Learning Outcomes :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Design detailed reports from multiple sets of data through a variety of sources.<br />&bull; Manipulate the data within your reports to suit your business needs.<br />&bull; Extract data from your reports to use in different functions and formulas.<br />&bull; Create an attractive chart and diagram for your business reports to help illustrate data<br />&bull; Learn the concepts of gathering, cleaning and storage of data.<br />&bull; Come up with multiple scenarios to resolve business problems within extracted data.<br />&bull; Design a data model for your large data groups.<br />&bull; Mine and uncover hidden information with DAX.<br />&bull; Use Power Queries and practice shaping, blending and exploring files in Excel`s.<br />query editor , and create completely automated loading procedures inside of Excel.<br />&bull; Use Power Pivot and DAX to explore and analyze our Excel data model.</p>', '<p>Dates : 17,19,21,24,26 &amp; 28 July 2022&nbsp;</p>', 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(249, 'Tele sales Professional', 400, '2022-07-03', '2022-07-07', '14:00:00', '15:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1652265128.png', 16, 0, '2022-05-11 10:32:08', '2022-02-22 18:48:07', NULL, '<p>Dates : 03, 04,05 , 06 &amp; 07 July 2022&nbsp;</p>', 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(250, 'Compensation & Benefits', 700, '2022-07-03', '2022-07-07', '14:00:00', '17:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645555865.PNG', 19, 0, '2022-05-11 10:26:51', '2022-02-22 18:51:05', '<p>&bull; In this workshop, you will learn about the only part of human resources that<br />works behind the scenes.<br />Compensation and benefits is usually a function that professionals in the field<br />typically avoid for its seemingly complex nature and dependency on<br />mathematics.</p>\r\n<p>&bull; When you attend this Workshop, you will change your mind about this HR<br />specialty. We will explain the specifics of compensation and benefits in such a<br />way that you be able to apply them easily at work.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Explain the basic principles and major elements of<br />compensation<br />&bull;Apply the various processes in compensation: job analysis, job<br />descriptions and job evaluation<br />&bull;Explain what constitutes a sound and effective compensation<br />and benefits program<br />&bull;Describe the basic compensation survey process</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Dates : 03, 04,05 , 06 &amp; 07 July 2022&nbsp;</p>', 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(251, 'The Super Communicator', 400, '2022-07-17', '2022-07-19', '11:00:00', '15:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1652264598.png', 9, 0, '2022-05-11 10:23:18', '2022-02-22 18:54:27', '<p>People who fail to develop communication skills often have their careers<br />stagnate or plateau in the mid-range.<br />But what is Communication? And why is it so important?<br />Now, in the 21st Century; Communication is no longer only about transmitting<br />information; it is more about achieving desired goals and results sooner than<br />later. This highly interactive workshop covers a vast array of communication<br />needs and scenarios that help the learners cultivate a set of advanced<br />communication skills that are essential in preparing individuals for the modern<br />agile world of today. A major goal of this workshop is to help the learners<br />understand the impact their communication skills have on other people. They will<br />also explore how improving these skills can make it easier for them to get along<br />in the workplace, and in life</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Identify common communication problems that may be holding you back<br />&bull; Apply Mehrabian&rsquo;s 55-38-7 rule in day-to-day Communication<br />&bull; Learn what your non-verbal messages are telling others<br />&bull; Identify Personal Communication Style &amp; Others&rsquo;<br />&bull; Use Communication to handle challenging conversations<br />&bull; Deal with situations assertively<br />&bull; Enhance Team Collaboration through Effective Communication</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Dates : 17,18 &amp; 19 July 2022</p>', 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(252, 'Writing Like Pro', 430, '2022-07-17', '2022-07-20', '19:00:00', '22:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1652264525.png', 13, 0, '2022-05-11 10:22:05', '2022-02-22 18:56:55', '<p>&bull; The clearer &amp; more concise a message is, the more likely it can resolve a<br />complex situation.<br />&bull; This workshop is designed to provide learners with advanced key business<br />writing tools for better &amp; more powerful impact.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Recognize the importance of setting an objective that<br />compliments the purpose of your writing<br />&bull; Apply the essential tools for effective business writing<br />&bull; Develop a personal writing style<br />&bull; Design a written document &amp; demonstrate the value of visual<br />aids &amp; style<br />&bull; Apply proofreading skills to ensure accuracy<br />&bull; Identify a challenging situation &amp; respond to it accordingly</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Dates : 17,18,19 &amp; 20 July 2022</p>', 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(253, 'Analytical Thinking', 430, '2022-07-24', '2022-07-27', '13:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1652264474.jpg', 9, 0, '2022-05-11 10:21:14', '2022-02-22 19:02:01', '<p>In today&rsquo;s society, many people experience information overload. We are<br />bombarded with messages to believe various ideas, purchase things, support<br />causes, and lead our lifestyle in a particular way. How do you know what to<br />believe? How do you separate the truth from the myths?<br />The answer lies in analytical &amp; critical thinking skills. The ability to clearly reason<br />through problems and to present arguments in a logical, compelling way has<br />become a key skill for survival in today&rsquo;s world. This highly interactive workshop<br />will give you some practical tools and hands-on experience with critical thinking<br />and problem solving.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Define core concepts of analytical thinking</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Describe other thinking styles, including left/right brain thinking and whole-<br />brain thinking</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Work through the analytical thinking process to build or analyze arguments<br />&bull; Develop and evaluate explanations<br />&bull; Improve key analytical thinking skills, including active listening and<br />questioning<br />&bull; Prepare and present powerful arguments</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Dates : 24,25,26 &amp; 27 Jluy 2022</p>', 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(254, 'The Alpha Leader', 500, '2022-07-31', '2022-08-03', '10:00:00', '14:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645556838.PNG', 12, 1, '2022-08-04 08:54:41', '2022-02-22 19:07:19', '<p>&bull; This highly interactive workshop is designed to prepare an Alpha Leader<br />through providing hands-on tools that ensure full understanding and<br />comprehension of the role of a leader as a source of empowerment for the<br />team, hence enhancing the overall team performance &amp; organizational<br />success.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Identify Personality Styles &amp; how to win with different styles<br />&bull; Link Leadership Styles with Maturity Levels of employees<br />&bull; Develop key management competencies required for the execution of<br />basics tasks and activities<br />&bull; Set SMART Goals and evaluate performance against them<br />&bull; Use Time Management Matrix to set priorities<br />&bull; Apply coaching techniques to boost productivity and optimize outcomes<br />&bull; Demonstrate skills of Strategic Leaders</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Dates : 31 July,01, 02&amp; 03 August 2022</p>', 'Virtual', 'eg', 0),
(255, 'The Alpha Leader', 500, '2022-07-31', '2022-08-03', '11:00:00', '15:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645973520.jpg', 12, 0, '2022-05-11 10:19:50', '2022-02-22 19:07:27', '<p>&bull; This highly interactive workshop is designed to prepare an Alpha Leader<br />through providing hands-on tools that ensure full understanding and<br />comprehension of the role of a leader as a source of empowerment for the<br />team, hence enhancing the overall team performance &amp; organizational<br />success.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Identify Personality Styles &amp; how to win with different styles<br />&bull; Link Leadership Styles with Maturity Levels of employees<br />&bull; Develop key management competencies required for the execution of<br />basics tasks and activities<br />&bull; Set SMART Goals and evaluate performance against them<br />&bull; Use Time Management Matrix to set priorities<br />&bull; Apply coaching techniques to boost productivity and optimize outcomes<br />&bull; Demonstrate skills of Strategic Leaders</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Dates : 31 July,01, 02&amp; 03 August 2022</p>', 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(256, 'Excel Master - Advanced Level', 200, '2022-08-06', '2022-08-20', '12:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1652264334.jpg', 14, 0, '2022-05-11 10:18:55', '2022-02-22 19:10:23', '<p>&bull; This Workshop is designed to focus on the advanced<br />Excel tools And features that goes beyond the basics<br />and enable users to go from only editing and formatting<br />sheets to creating their own Advanced calculations and<br />reports instead of working one Previously prepared<br />ones<br />&bull; Also you will check in this workshop the different<br />powerful tools that make you the Master of Excel</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Mastering Excel most important functions<br />&bull; Analyzing Data and Alternative data sets<br />&bull; Apply the key Excel functions to prepare data for analysis<br />&bull; Apply advanced calculations<br />&bull; Create and customize pivot tables to reconcile and analyze<br />accounts efficiently<br />&bull; Utilize pivot tables functions and calculations to generate a<br />set of management and business analysis reports<br />&bull; Creating Advanced charts and graphics<br />&bull; Changing workbook Appearance</p>', '<p>Dates : 06,13 &amp; 20 August 2022&nbsp;</p>', 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(257, 'Principles of Successful Negotiations', 430, '2022-08-07', '2022-08-10', '14:00:00', '17:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1652264263.png', 9, 0, '2022-05-11 10:17:43', '2022-02-22 19:14:32', '<p>&bull; Knowing how to negotiate effectively, and with confidence, is a skill that will<br />change everything. This highly interactive workshop is designed to provide<br />participants with the essential knowledge &amp; tools they need to know about<br />negotiation, step by methodical step. They&rsquo;ll also be armed with a set of<br />practical tools that you can start using right away to get better results in their<br />work and life in general.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Define Negotiation &amp; highlight its importance<br />&bull; Identify different negotiation models &amp; styles &amp; when to use each<br />&bull; Using a set of effective skills for better negotiation outcomes<br />&bull; Discover the appropriate negotiation style for each situation<br />&bull; Identify personal negotiation style &amp; other&rsquo;s</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Dates : 07,08,09 &amp; 10 August 2022&nbsp;</p>', 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(258, 'Setting Budget and Forecasting', 430, '2022-08-14', '2022-08-16', '12:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1652264087.png', 17, 0, '2022-05-11 10:14:48', '2022-02-22 19:16:48', '<p>The primary challenge faced by organizations and managers today is to<br />creatively solve business problems. The principles of management have been<br />categorized into the four major functions of planning, organizing, leading, and<br />controlling popularly known as the P-O-L-C framework; Planning, Organizing,<br />Leading &amp; Controlling.<br />The highly interactive workshop focuses closely at 3 elements of the P.O.L.C<br />Framework, which are; Planning, Organizing &amp; Controlling. It provide a step by<br />step guide to plan for a project that gets results. It is designed to equip the<br />participants with the essential skills needed to fulfill their responsibilities in a<br />professional way. The concepts, methods and techniques presented include both<br />well established and latest thinking to provide the essential knowledge, skills,<br />and toolkit to ensure more successful outcomes.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Apply a professional, systematic approach to planning and employing the<br />\'SMART\' criteria to objectives setting<br />&bull; Produce realistic plans, determine the critical path, and manage risks<br />&bull; Use environmental scanning, budgeting, and breakeven analysis as tools for<br />planning and forecasting<br />&bull; Define planning tools &amp; techniques such as \'Gantt\' charts and \'Load\' charts<br />&bull; Recognize the importance of control, and of properly utilizing key<br />performance measures to keep work on track<br />&bull; Mobilize resources, accurately monitor project performance, and maintain<br />control of the project<br />&bull; Assess the impact of organizational change and manage people\'s resistance<br />to change</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Dates : 14,15,&amp; 16 August 2022&nbsp;</p>', 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(259, 'Purchasing & Cost Saving Techniques', 430, '2022-08-16', '2022-08-18', '12:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1652263968.png', 18, 0, '2022-05-11 10:12:49', '2022-02-22 19:18:55', NULL, '<p>Dates : 16,17 &amp; 18 August 2022</p>', 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(260, 'Selling Skills', 430, '2022-08-21', '2022-08-23', '12:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1652263879.png', 16, 0, '2022-05-11 10:11:19', '2022-02-22 19:21:03', '<p>&bull; This Workshop provides participants with core knowledge about sales as a<br />function and as a process; this means that participants will get solid exposure<br />to sales and its contribution to company growth. In addition, participants will<br />acquire several skills related to negotiating deals, overcoming obstacles,<br />resolving customer issues and closing sales.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Identify and adopt the right professional selling behaviors and skills needed<br />to maximize sales performance<br />&bull; Develop critical self-driven practices to optimize personal and business<br />effectiveness and efficiency<br />&bull; Master and implement the sales process to successfully handle objections<br />and close more deals<br />&bull; Manage customer expectations and exceed it to gain customer loyalty and<br />generate repeat business<br />&bull; Master the art of verbal and non-verbal communication to create<br />atmosphere of respect and trust in the seller-buyer interface</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Dates : 21,22,23 August 2022</p>', 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(261, 'Handling Customer Complains', 400, '2022-08-22', '2022-08-25', '14:00:00', '17:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1652263784.png', 15, 0, '2022-05-11 10:09:44', '2022-02-22 19:24:55', '<p>Handling difficult customers can be a challenging task especially if it is<br />charged with irrational emotion. Often, the natural reaction would be to feel<br />defensive and try explaining why the situation occurred. More often than not,<br />this kind of reaction only make the situation go worse. This workshop is<br />designed to help the participants get into of their customers, understand their<br />pain and expectation, understand their preferences &amp; priorities, in order to<br />deliver a service that exceeds their expectations and fulfill both their<br />materialistic &amp; emotional needs.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull;Define customer service and how to use this understanding to CS in handling<br />customers<br />&bull;Use the RATER Framework to enhance the Customers experience<br />&bull;Develop a Customer Journey Map<br />&bull;Describe the essential skillset for CS<br />&bull;Identify the four types of customers and how to handle each effectively</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Dates : 22,23,24 &amp; 25 August 2022</p>', 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(262, 'Your First 90 Days as a Manager', 430, '2022-08-28', '2022-09-04', '14:00:00', '17:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1652263707.png', 12, 0, '2022-05-11 10:08:28', '2022-02-22 19:28:04', '<p>&bull; As long as there have been leaders, there have been leadership transitions.<br />The changes challenges these transitions impose on the new leader are as<br />old as human society. Those challenges have not gotten any easier. On the<br />contrary, the complexity of modern organizations and the speed at which<br />business gets conducted have seemingly added to it. This highly interactive<br />workshop is your roadmap for taking charge in your first 90 days in your new<br />position as a newly promoted manager. Why do you need it? Because<br />transitions are critical times when small differences in your actions can have<br />huge impacts on results.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Describe &amp; develop new leadership competencies<br />&bull; Conduct a personal SWOT assessment to expand on the strengths &amp;<br />improve the weaknesses<br />&bull; Follow a 90-days action plan overcome the promotion challenge<br />&bull; Use the ADEPT Model to place people in the right roles &amp; provide the<br />right support<br />&bull; Define Decision-making styles &amp; employ each style according to the<br />situation</p>', '<p>Dates : 28,29,30,31 Aug,01 &amp; 04 Sep 2022</p>', 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(263, 'The Pro Recruiter', 500, '2022-08-07', '2022-08-09', '11:00:00', '15:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1652263386.jpg', 19, 0, '2022-05-11 10:03:07', '2022-02-22 19:30:51', '<p>Build your strategic aspects of this important HR function. In this workshop It will show<br />you the logical and correct steps you must take to structure and implement<br />recruitment and selection practices and how to be a professional recruiter.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Define recruitment and selection and the important role this function plays in the<br />success of an organization<br />&bull; List the main steps that should be followed to develop an effective recruitment plan<br />and select the best methods and sources for attracting qualified candidates<br />&bull; Choose the most appropriate techniques for short listing and assessing candidates<br />considering the reliability and validity of each<br />&bull; Implement the right measures and Key Performance Indicators (KPIs) to evaluate<br />the effectiveness of recruitment efforts</p>', '<p>Dates : 07,08 &amp; 09 August 2022</p>', 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(264, 'Supervisory Skills', 430, '2022-08-21', '2022-08-23', '19:00:00', '22:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1652263327.png', 12, 0, '2022-05-11 10:02:07', '2022-02-22 19:35:53', '<p>The workshop is designed to provide learners with highly effective tools &amp;<br />techniques that improve the essential supervisory skills your team needs,<br />both managerial &amp; people&rsquo;s skills - to strengthen teamwork, team<br />performance &amp; organizational success.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Identify the supervision functions<br />&bull; Create a planning network diagram<br />&bull; Describe the elements of planning<br />&bull; Apply the principles &amp;amp; approaches of organizing work<br />&bull; Use IDEALS Delegation Model to empower the team<br />&bull; Describe the control process, types &amp;amp; challenges<br />&bull; Apply tools to fix team performance<br />&bull; Demonstrate coaching skills &amp;amp; mentoring characteristics</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Dates : 21,22,23 August 2022</p>', 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(265, 'Self Awareness & Self Confidence', 400, '2022-08-14', '2022-08-17', '19:00:00', '22:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1652263186.png', 9, 0, '2022-05-11 09:59:46', '2022-02-22 19:39:04', '<p>Healthy self-esteem and self-confidence are essential for growth and achieving<br />success. Of all the judgments you make in life, none is as important as the one<br />you make about yourself. Without some measure of self-worth, life can be painful<br />and unrelenting. This highly interactive workshop is designed to help the learners<br />discover some techniques that can help them feel better about themselves and<br />improve their self-esteem and self-confidence.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Describe the four archetypes of Self-awareness<br />&bull; Process emotions in healthy ways &amp; develop Emotional Agility<br />&bull; Develop techniques for eliminating unhealthy thought patterns and replacing<br />them with supportive patterns<br />&bull; Act more assertively and understand why this is important to self-esteem<br />&bull; and self-confidence<br />&bull; Deal with setbacks in a way that does not damage self-esteem<br />&bull; Set goals that reflect your dreams and desires and reinforce healthy patterns</p>', '<p>Dates : 14,15,16 &amp; 17 August 2022&nbsp;</p>', 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(266, 'Crucial Conversation', 500, '2022-08-28', '2022-08-31', '19:00:00', '22:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1652263139.jpg', 9, 0, '2022-05-11 09:58:59', '2022-02-22 19:42:32', '<p>&bull; Many &lsquo;defining&rsquo; moments in life come from having crucial conversations,<br />which we anticipate will be difficult and which we may feel ill-equipped to<br />handle. We may also occasionally be involved in amicable conversations that<br />suddenly turn sour. Having the knowledge and confidence to deal with these<br />situations can make all the difference between a relationship fortified and a<br />relationship lost, or a sale made, and a sale lost.<br />&bull; This interactive workshop focuses on techniques on how to hold such<br />conversations in a positive space when surrounded by highly charged<br />emotions. It is designed to equip you with both the skillset and the confidence<br />you need to successfully manage crucial conversations and ensure that both<br />sides have the best chance of leaving the encounter feeling happy.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p> Define &amp; detect a Crucial Conversation<br /> Assess your usual approach to stress<br /> Recognize the power of Dialogue<br /> Recognize personal dialogue patterns &amp; change it into positive stories<br /> Use S.T.A.T.E &amp; AAMP techniques to tell your story &amp; learn the path of<br />others<br /> Handle disagreements effectively using the ABC Method<br /> Describe and practice methods to move from conversation to actions and<br />results</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Dates : 28,29,30 &amp; 31 August 2022</p>', 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(267, 'Your Business Writing Mojo!', 430, '2022-08-28', '2022-08-31', '13:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1652263074.jpg', 13, 0, '2022-05-11 09:57:55', '2022-02-22 19:45:54', '<p>&bull; In business writing, the language is concrete, the point of view is clear,<br />and the points are well expressed.<br />&bull; This workshop is designed to provide the learners with a proven step-by-step<br />process, to write faster and more effectively.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Apply the basic tools of writing for effective outcome<br />&bull; Understand and master the punctuation &amp;amp; spelling techniques for<br />better Business writing<br />&bull; Develop a technical writing style<br />&bull; Identify the different types of writing<br />&bull; Avoid common mistakes in technical writing<br />&bull; Demonstrate an understanding of formal language required for business<br />communication</p>', '<p>Dates : 28,29,30 &amp; 31 August 2022</p>', 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(268, 'Email Writing Techniques', 430, '2022-09-04', '2022-09-07', '14:00:00', '17:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1652263006.png', 13, 0, '2022-05-11 09:56:46', '2022-02-22 19:49:13', '<p>In business writing, the language is concrete, the point of view is clear, and the<br />points are well expressed. This workshop is designed to provide the learners<br />with a proven step-by-step process, to write faster and more effectively.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Apply the basic tools of writing for effective outcome<br />&bull; Develop a technical writing style<br />&bull; Identify the different types of writing<br />&bull; Avoid common mistakes in technical writing<br />&bull; Demonstrate an understanding of formal language required for business<br />Communication</p>', '<p>Dates : 04,05,06 &amp; 07 Sep 2022&nbsp;</p>', 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(269, 'The Alpha Leader', 500, '2022-09-11', '2022-09-14', '12:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1652262940.jpg', 12, 0, '2022-05-11 09:55:40', '2022-02-22 19:51:44', '<p>&bull; This highly interactive workshop is designed to prepare an Alpha Leader<br />through providing hands-on tools that ensure full understanding and<br />comprehension of the role of a leader as a source of empowerment for the<br />team, hence enhancing the overall team performance &amp; organizational<br />success.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Identify Personality Styles &amp; how to win with different styles<br />&bull; Link Leadership Styles with Maturity Levels of employees<br />&bull; Develop key management competencies required for the execution of<br />basics tasks and activities<br />&bull; Set SMART Goals and evaluate performance against them<br />&bull; Use Time Management Matrix to set priorities<br />&bull; Apply coaching techniques to boost productivity and optimize outcomes<br />&bull; Demonstrate skills of Strategic Leaders</p>', '<p>Dates : 11,12,13 &amp; 14 Sep 2022&nbsp;</p>', 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(270, 'Public Speaking : Express to Impress ( By SPS )', 600, '2022-09-11', '2022-09-22', '20:00:00', '23:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1652262895.png', 9, 0, '2022-05-11 09:54:55', '2022-02-22 19:54:33', '<p>◘ As young professional seeking excellence in your professional world, public<br />speaking is a vital skill to your success and your business as well. You won&rsquo;t be<br />concerned anymore about how to overcome challenges in presenting yourself<br />and your ideas in different situations.<br />◘ Whether it&rsquo;s a meeting with your managers and co-workers or communicating<br />with other departments and customers on behalf of your entity. And because<br />Such situations require a powerful set of skills to be able to express and<br />impress!<br />◘ In our program, we will help you gaining all these required skills which will<br />positively impact all other elements of your professional development journey<br />to establish yourself as a valuable member in your organization.<br />◘ You will gain more confidence in yourself by mastering your verbal and<br />nonverbal communication aspects, asking the right questions to understand<br />and validate the received information.<br />◘ You will be able to do more with less saving the most valuable asset &ldquo;Time&rdquo;. By<br />learning effective research techniques collecting as many relevant information<br />to your topic, how to analyze and organize your ideas to structure your speech<br />effectively matching your audience.</p>', '<p>Dates : 11,13,15,18,20 &amp; 22 Sep 2022</p>', 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(271, 'Advanced  Sales Professional', 500, '2022-08-18', '2022-08-29', '14:00:00', '17:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1652262812.png', 16, 0, '2022-05-11 09:53:32', '2022-02-22 19:57:48', '<p>&bull; This Workshop provides participants with core knowledge about sales as a<br />function and as a process; this means that participants will get solid exposure<br />to sales and its contribution to company growth.<br />&bull; In addition, participants will acquire several skills related to negotiating deals,<br />overcoming obstacles, resolving customer issues and closing sales.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :</p>\r\n<p>● Identify and adopt the right professional selling behaviors and skills<br />needed to maximize sales performance<br />● Develop critical self-driven practices to optimize personal and<br />business effectiveness and efficiency<br />● Master and implement the sales process to successfully handle<br />objections and close more deals<br />● Manage customer expectations and exceed it to gain customer<br />loyalty and generate repeat business<br />● Master the art of verbal and non-verbal communication to create<br />an atmosphere of respect and trust in the seller-buyer interface</p>', '<p>Dates : 18,20,22,25 , 27 &amp; 29 Sep 2022</p>', 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(272, 'Successful Thinking & Planning', 200, '2022-09-20', '2022-09-22', '12:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1652262736.png', 10, 0, '2022-05-11 09:52:17', '2022-02-22 20:00:40', '<p>&bull; In this workshop, we will cover the steps of the strategy management<br />process, starting with the \'thinking\' components of strategy, moving into the<br />\'planning\' components and ending with \'execution\',<br />&bull; Participants will be able to implement or improve the strategic process at their<br />organizations to reach their vision and achieve their mission.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>● Apply strategic thinking to analyze their current environment and<br />determine their organizational ambition<br />● Employ the strategic management process to best achieve the desired<br />ambition<br />● Assess and choose strategies that create a sustainable competitive<br />advantage for the organization<br />● Determine strategic objectives, Key Performance Indicators (KPIs)<br />and \'SMART\' targets for the organization<br />● Convert strategic plans to operating plans through creating strategic<br />initiatives and sequencing activities</p>', '<p>Dates : 20,21 &amp; 22 Sep 2022</p>', 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(273, 'Accountability & Ownership', 400, '2022-09-25', '2022-09-27', '12:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1652262586.png', 9, 0, '2022-05-11 09:49:46', '2022-02-22 20:03:24', '<p>&bull; It&rsquo;s no wonder that organizations who promote accountability<br />are more successful and more productive. In this Employee<br />Accountability workshop.<br />&bull; You will learn about what accountability is how to promote it in<br />your organization, and how to become more accountable to<br />yourself and others.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>● Understand what accountability is and what events in history have<br />shaped our view of it<br />● Identify the requirements for personal and corporate accountability<br />● Apply the cycle of accountability and the fundamental elements required<br />to build an accountable organization<br />● Describe what individuals must do to become accountable<br />● Build skills required for accountability, including goal setting, giving and<br />receiving<br />● feedback, and delegation<br />● Pinpoint ways to build ownership in your organization<br />● Isolate areas for further self-improvement</p>', '<p>Dates : 25 , 26 &amp; 27 Sep 2022&nbsp;</p>', 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(274, 'Setting KPI`s & Managing Performance', 430, '2022-09-11', '2022-09-13', '12:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1652262501.png', 19, 0, '2022-05-11 09:48:22', '2022-02-22 20:06:55', '<p>&bull; This workshop addresses the three cornerstones of<br />excellent performance namely, the right set of Key<br />Performance Indicators (KPIs), the proper means of<br />tracking progress and the most effective methodologies<br />for intervention and feedback.</p>\r\n<p>&bull; By learning how to skillfully handle each of these tasks,<br />team leaders, supervisors or managers will be able to<br />directly and positively influence performance in their<br />units, sections, or departments.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; List the main criteria for measuring performance and use them to plan<br />and manage the performance of others<br />&bull; Design reporting mechanisms which are critical for measuring progress<br />and use them to track performance and determine critical deviations<br />&bull; Provide effective feedback as a means of dealing with individual<br />performance gaps and as a tool for effectively addressing all unfavorable<br />changes in performance<br />&bull; Determine when to coach and when to counsel and then do so based on<br />a thorough understanding of performance gaps and their root causes</p>', '<p>Dates : 11, 12 &amp; 13 Sep 2022</p>', 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(275, 'Dynamic Presentations (BY SPS)', 600, '2022-09-11', '2022-09-13', '12:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1652262177.png', 9, 0, '2022-05-11 09:42:57', '2022-02-22 20:09:52', '<p>◘ As an expert in the information you&rsquo;re presenting, you have to find a way to<br />support your message in an entertaining way.</p>\r\n<p>◘ Either you are presenting data you received via reports, dashboards, and<br />systems to your peers or the top management to help them taking a decision<br />or to find a solution Or presenting a new process or a strategic plan for your<br />team ,so that employees understand how their work contributes to the overall<br />strategy.</p>\r\n<p>◘ Dynamic presentation program will help you switch the boring rigid static<br />presentation into an interesting highly engaging dynamic one, to have the<br />advantage of perfectly responsive design for your information and your<br />presentation will go much smoother. Not only will your audience be<br />impressed, but they are going to even be pulled in by your message.</p>\r\n<p>◘ In this program you will be introduced to a set of techniques and tools for the<br />transformation of raw data into meaningful ,useful information in an<br />interesting dynamic highly engaging way.</p>\r\n<p>◘ You will learn How to display data the right way in your Presentations A<br />Context plays a huge role in how best to render data by first asking yourself &ldquo;<br />Am I Presenting Or Circulating My Data?&rdquo; &ldquo;What Message Am I Trying To<br />Convey? &ldquo;</p>\r\n<p>◘ This program will help you presenting your personal brand by mastering the<br />way you are presenting .presenting your points with power, not just<br />PowerPoint</p>', '<p>Dates : 11, 12 &amp; 13 Sep 2022</p>', 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(276, 'Business Agility', 700, '2022-09-04', '2022-09-07', '19:00:00', '22:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645973481.png', 11, 0, '2022-05-11 09:42:21', '2022-02-22 20:14:07', '<p>The shortest and briefest definition of Agility is the inherent ability to respond to<br />change. But does that mean in Business World?<br />Can you think of a company that has gone bust? Nokia, Kodak? You&rsquo;ve probably heard<br />of more examples, there are loads of them out there! Big names like these have failed<br />to cope with the rapid changes and therefore were doomed to fail.<br />Now, more than ever before, organizations need to reinvent themselves to cope with<br />the ever-changing nature of the workplace.<br />This highly interactive workshop is designed to raise the participants&rsquo; awareness of<br />Business Agility &amp; it&rsquo;s best practices. The learning process is based on real-world<br />business cases like McDonalds, Panadol, Mazda, Apple, Harley Davidson &amp; more.<br />Participants will also acquire the knowledge &amp; tools needed to create an action plan to<br />meet ambiguity with agility in order implement new approaches such as Business<br />Model Canvas &amp; Blue Ocean Strategy that transforms an undesired situation into an<br />opportunity.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Recognize the importance of leading agile and resilient organizations during<br />turbulent times<br />&bull; Make decisions in chaotic situations<br />&bull; Use problem solving tools to provide effective solutions<br />&bull; Identify ambiguity in business and adapt it to agility<br />&bull; Lead and develop proactive mechanisms to withstand environmental<br />disruptions<br />&bull; Create compelling strategies to lead and drive agility and resilience<br />&bull; Use Business Model Canvas &amp; Blue Ocean Strategy to create value<br />&bull; Demonstrate agile leadership skills in the modern world</p>', '<p>Dates : 04,05,06 &amp; 07 Sep 2022</p>', 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(277, 'Your 720 Min Guide for Time Management', 400, '2022-09-18', '2022-09-20', '11:00:00', '15:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1652262108.jpg', 9, 0, '2022-05-11 09:41:48', '2022-02-22 20:16:45', '<p>&bull; This interactive workshop is designed to help the<br />participants explore various time management skills and<br />stress management techniques to get better control and<br />have a more positive impact over their time at the<br />professional and social levels.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Identify time management challenges and assess their efficiency in managing their time<br />&bull; Use Time Management Matrix for better time management<br />&bull; Analyze stress symptoms and their causes in order to identify their negative impact<br />&bull; Recognize Delegation rules &amp; tools<br />&bull; Apply time-saving techniques to stop wasting time<br />&bull; Apply STOP practice in stressful situations</p>', '<p>Dates : 18,19 &amp; 20 Sep 2022</p>', 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(278, 'Design Thinking - Unlock Innovation', 500, '2022-09-25', '2022-09-28', '19:00:00', '22:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1652262067.png', 9, 0, '2022-05-11 09:41:07', '2022-02-22 20:19:36', '<p>Design thinking is a powerful process of problem solving, a journey that begins<br />with having an empathic understanding of unmet customer needs. From that<br />insight emerges a blend of Heart, Head and Hand process that is based on<br />vision,<br />continuing on to development, applied creativity, prototyping then diving into<br />experimentation, practical creation &amp;amp; testing. This highly interactive<br />workshop is<br />designed to help the participants learn a proven, systematic approach to new<br />product development through a process that puts unmet customer needs at the<br />center of the problem. It also helps them apply design thinking approaches to<br />business, so that the success rate for innovation can improve substantially.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Use Design Thinking to solve problems more creatively<br />&bull; Understand problems from the customers perspective<br />&bull; Apply different brainstorming techniques to identify innovative ideas<br />&bull; Use effective design research<br />&bull; Understand the value of creating prototypes to test your ideas<br />&bull; Keep your design ideas moving forward</p>', '<p>Dates : 25,26,27 &amp; 28 Sep 2022&nbsp;</p>', 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(279, 'Finance For Non - Financials', 430, '2022-09-25', '2022-09-27', '11:00:00', '15:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1652262023.png', 17, 0, '2022-05-11 09:40:24', '2022-02-22 20:22:21', '<p>&bull; This Workshop transforms financial and accounting concepts into<br />decision making tools you can unsuccessfully every day. You will<br />learn to apply the fundamentals of finance to improve budget<br />management, increase potential profits, and assess the financial<br />performance of business activities. You will also understand the<br />terminology used by accounting and finance staff and will feel<br />more confident when being involved with them or using them<br />&bull; Professionals/Managers with a financial background are considered<br />most efficient at managing any operating scenario. Knowledge of<br />financial aspects that help in decision making is the key to their<br />success. It is important for a senior professional to be equipped with<br />financial decision-making tools to be able to analyze financial<br />statements, understand the nature of cost and ways to reduce cost,<br />take pricing decisions, decide a product mix and opt for the best<br />suited option of financing the need.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Define the four key financial statements: balance sheet,<br />income statement, cash flow and changes in owner equity<br />&bull; Interpret the financial health and condition of a<br />company, division or responsibility center and use<br />financial information for management and evaluation<br />&bull; Distinguish between accounting and finance and<br />explain the finance role in running businesses<br />&bull; Prepare a company\'s operating budget and relate it to<br />the organization\'s strategic objectives<br />&bull; Apply Financial techniques to enhance decision making</p>', '<p>Dates : 25,26 &amp; 27 Sep 2022</p>', 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(280, 'Project Management', 700, '2022-10-02', '2022-10-18', '12:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1652261836.png', 10, 0, '2022-05-11 09:37:17', '2022-02-22 20:26:19', '<p>&bull; The overall aim of this workshop is to provide participants with the necessary<br />skills required to plan their projects by creating project scope statements and<br />project work breakdown structures. Additionally, participants will learn how to<br />develop key performance indicators for monitoring and controlling their project<br />schedule and budget.<br />&bull; The workshop also aims at assisting participants in appraising the feasibility<br />of their projects by applying capital budgeting techniques. Finally, the<br />workshop will cover how to effectively plan project stakeholders&rsquo; engagement<br />and manage their expectations.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p> Plan projects using statement of work and Work Breakdown Structure<br />(WBS)<br /> Schedule projects activities and build the project network model<br /> Calculate project budgets and schedule variances using Earned Value<br />(EV) Techniques<br /> Select the right projects using capital budgeting techniques<br /> Relate to project stakeholders through better negotiation and<br />communication skills</p>', '<p>Dates : 02,04,09,11,16 &amp; 18 October 2022&nbsp;</p>', 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(281, 'The Super Communicator', 400, '2022-10-17', '2022-10-20', '14:00:00', '17:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1652261773.png', 9, 0, '2022-05-11 09:36:13', '2022-02-22 20:28:57', '<p>People who fail to develop communication skills often have their careers<br />stagnate or plateau in the mid-range.<br />But what is Communication? And why is it so important?<br />Now, in the 21st Century; Communication is no longer only about transmitting<br />information; it is more about achieving desired goals and results sooner than<br />later. This highly interactive workshop covers a vast array of communication<br />needs and scenarios that help the learners cultivate a set of advanced<br />communication skills that are essential in preparing individuals for the modern<br />agile world of today. A major goal of this workshop is to help the learners<br />understand the impact their communication skills have on other people. They will<br />also explore how improving these skills can make it easier for them to get along<br />in the workplace, and in life</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Identify common communication problems that may be holding you back<br />&bull; Apply Mehrabian&rsquo;s 55-38-7 rule in day-to-day Communication<br />&bull; Learn what your non-verbal messages are telling others<br />&bull; Identify Personal Communication Style &amp; Others&rsquo;<br />&bull; Use Communication to handle challenging conversations<br />&bull; Deal with situations assertively<br />&bull; Enhance Team Collaboration through Effective Communication</p>', '<p>Dates : 17,18,19 &amp; 20 Oct 2022&nbsp;</p>', 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(282, 'Cost Analysis, Control and Optimization', 430, '2022-10-17', '2022-10-20', '14:00:00', '17:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1652261719.png', 17, 0, '2022-05-11 09:35:19', '2022-02-22 20:32:31', '<p>&bull; The main objective of any cost management training is activity-based costing<br />which helps in making better decisions.<br />&bull; Among these decisions are whether to drop or keep a product, make or buy,<br />and replace or keep a piece of equipment. Moreover, cost management<br />includes allocating costs of service departments internally.<br />&bull; Also covered in this workshop techniques of cost reduction and how to use<br />them</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Discover the importance of analyzing and managing costs<br />&bull; Develop important tools for planning and decision making<br />&bull; Explain Activity-Based Costing (ABC) and Activity-Based Management<br />(ABM)<br />&bull; Estimate costs and allocate them properly<br />&bull; Evaluate and manage performance through strategic cost management<br />&bull; Apply several cost reduction strategies in order to meet changing global,<br />statutory and market conditions<br />&bull; Recognize and apply measuring initiatives and set targets in order to<br />improve productivity</p>', '<p>Dates : 17,18,19 &amp; 20 Oct 2022&nbsp;</p>', 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(283, 'Business Model Canvas', 500, '2022-10-02', '2022-10-05', '13:00:00', '16:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645694853.png', 11, 0, '2022-05-11 09:34:01', '2022-02-22 20:35:02', '<p>&bull; In this workshop If you\'re improving an existing<br />business or launching something new, you\'re facing<br />one big challenge. How do you take decisions, test them<br />and improve them through Business Model Canvas</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Understand the key concepts of Business Decisions<br />&bull; Acquire knowledge of the 9 building blocks of the Business<br />Model Canvas for value creation<br />&bull; Learn how to apply the Business Model Canvas to map out<br />your current business model for understanding and analysis.<br />&bull; Learn how to take different decisions based on Business<br />Model Canvas<br />&bull; Learn to align your decisions with Business Model Design<br />Space.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Dates : 02.03,04 &amp; 05 October 2022&nbsp;</p>', 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(284, 'Power Point Essential', 200, '2022-10-09', '2022-10-10', '18:00:00', '22:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1652261606.png', 14, 0, '2022-05-11 09:33:26', '2022-02-22 20:40:07', '<p>&bull; skill based training about creating and delivering<br />presentations using Microsoft PowerPoint. The trainees<br />will learn and apply presentation skills with PowerPoint,<br />starting from creating presentations from scratch and<br />ending with presenting effectively.<br />&bull; The training is aimed at business users, admins, and all<br />people who want to learn the PowerPoint basics and<br />powerful presentations skills and integrate them in their<br />work.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objectives :</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Creating wonderful presentations.<br />&bull; Organizing slide contents<br />&bull; Mastering animations and transitions.<br />&bull; Getting presentations done effectively.</p>', '<p>Dates : 09 &amp; 10 October 2022</p>', 'Virtual', 'sa', 0),
(285, 'Coaching Skills', 430, '2022-10-23', '2022-10-25', '11:00:00', '15:00:00', 100, 'images/courses/1645694772.png', 12, 0, '2022-05-11 09:30:19', '2022-02-22 20:43:06', '<p>Coach, Mentor, Role Model, Supporter, Guide... do these words ring a bell?<br />Being a coach involves being able to draw from several disciplines. Coaching is<br />based on a partnership that involves giving both support and challenging<br />opportunities to employees. Mentorship is a related skill that is often a part of<br />coaching. It&rsquo;s about being a guide, offering wisdom and advice when it is<br />needed.<br />This highly interactive workshop is designed with a purpose to provide the<br />learners with keys on how and when to coach (and when to use other tools, like<br />mentoring) is an essential skill that can benefit both; the learner and the<br />organization.</p>\r\n<p>Learning Objcetives :&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&bull; Understand how coaching can be used to develop your team.<br />&bull; Develop the coaching and mentoring skills that help improve individual<br />&bull; performance.<br />&bull; Demonstrate the behaviors and practices of an effective coach.<br />&bull; Recognize employees&rsquo; strengths and give them the feedback they need to<br />succeed.<br />&bull; Identify employee problems and ways you can help to correct them.</p>', '<p>Dates : 23,24 &amp; 25 October 2022</p>', 'Virtual', 'sa', 0);
