(1, 1, 'How to Integrate between Performance Management and your Training Plan?', NULL, '<p class=\"header-text\"><span style=\"font-family: \'arial black\', sans-serif;\">Through the session, we will explain how to create a successful performance management system and how the TNA and the employee\'s development plans should be embedded in this system from the very beginning to ensure the employees have all the competencies whether core, technical or behavioral to achieve the set objectives with the required Performance Standards.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'arial black\', sans-serif;\"><strong>The session will also identify many relative different perspectives and terminologies that have been used recently with the new trends and the markets changes worldwide.</strong></span></p>', '<h2><span style=\"font-family: \'arial black\', sans-serif; color: #feca40;\"><strong>Learning Outcome</strong></span></h2>\r\n<p><br /><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'arial black\', sans-serif;\">- Understand performance determinants and dimensions.</span></strong><br /><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'arial black\', sans-serif;\">- Understand the importance of well created and implemented Performance Management system.</span></strong><br /><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'arial black\', sans-serif;\">- Differentiate between Performance Management and Performance Appraisal.</span></strong><br /><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'arial black\', sans-serif;\">- Understand the Performance Management creation process.</span></strong><br /><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'arial black\', sans-serif;\">- Understand the integration between Performance Management and employees&rsquo; training and development as a continuous process.</span></strong><br /><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'arial black\', sans-serif;\">- Conduct TNA through the Performance Management process and outputs.</span></strong><br /><strong><span style=\"font-family: \'arial black\', sans-serif;\">- Create Development Plans through the Performance Management Process and outputs.</span></strong></p>', 'images/6209bc76487d7.jpg', 'images/6209bc76c6327.jpg', 'images/6209bc76ed1f3.jpg', '2022-01-22 00:01:03', '2022-02-14 23:50:15'),
(2, 2, 'FREE - Customer Centricity', '<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #0090d0;\">Developing Customer Centric Mindset</span></strong></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Do your employees know about the &ldquo;customer centricity&rdquo; approach?<br />Do your employees have a customer-centric mindset?<br />Do your employees know their role in deploying customer centricity in your organization, even though they are not directly dealing with customers?<br />Are you leading your teams upon customer-centric metrics and variables?<br />When you listen to someone mention &ldquo;customer centricity &ldquo;, what comes to your mind first?<br />Is it that you are already deploying customer centricity approach in your organization and in your daily tasks? Is it that it&rsquo;s an interesting approach and you can easily transform to that approach? Is it challenging and implanting it will have a high cost? does it worth it?</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #feca40;\">Why customer centricity?</span></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Since customer centricity is a wide-ranging strategy that requires businesses to focus all their attention and processes around the clients.&nbsp;<br />And such an approach has become inevitable for building a successful model to prosper and shine in today&rsquo;s modern, competitive, and highly dynamic world; we will help you answer these questions, and more &hellip;<br />We will provide all the skills and tools necessary to implement the above changes with the most efficient approaches and utilize the available resources so that you can make your company or government entity truly consumer-centric.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>\" If people like you,</strong><br /><strong>they\'ll listen to you, but</strong><br /><strong>if they trust you, they\'ll</strong><br /><strong>do business with you.\"</strong><br /><strong><span style=\"color: #feca40;\">-Zig Ziglar</span></strong></p>', '<h2><span style=\"color: #feca40;\"><strong>The Learning <span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">Objectives</span></strong></span></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Define the scope of customer service and measure its effectiveness to ensure repeat customer and corporate growth.</li>\r\n<li>Understand customer experience management to adapt to changing consumer expectations and create an awesome customer experience program.</li>\r\n<li>Define customer experience strategies and use empathy to create desirable products/services and great customer interactions.</li>\r\n<li>Measure customer experience performance to analyze problems and come up with recovery strategies and take corrective actions.</li>\r\n<li>Improve customer experience practices to continuously meet service challenges and instill a customer-centric culture.</li>\r\n</ul>', '<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"color: #feca40;\">How will this experience be different?</span></span></h2>\r\n<p>You will get exposure to both theoretical and practical parts so that you can quickly develop a customer-centric mindset; and apply this approach to your job, relying on our experiential activities; we guarantee you a hassle-free transformation.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /><br /><span style=\"background-color: #0090d0;\"><strong>&nbsp; Date of Free Sesion</strong><strong>:</strong> 30 August 2022&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></h5>\r\n<h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"background-color: #0090d0;\"><strong>&nbsp; Time:</strong><strong> </strong>11 AM to 2 PM | UAE Time&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><br /><br /><br /><br /></h5>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'arial black\', sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"background-color: #feca40;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;Register Now in the below&nbsp; &nbsp;<br /></span></strong></span></h2>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"color: #feca40;\">You Eligible to Invite 5 Members&nbsp; from your Team, Friends, connections</span></span></h4>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</h2>', 'images/62dfb36f44190.png', 'images/62e1068720035.png', 'images/62de8c65b3428.png', '2022-01-22 00:01:03', '2022-08-05 11:01:13');
